0during%20multi-engine%20training.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20classroom%20was%20dark%2C%20with%20the%20view%20projected%20onto%20a%20curved%20wall%20in%20front%20of%20the%20replica%20cockpit.%20I%20was%20helped%20along%20the%20way%20by%20Matthew%20Yemm%2C%20a%20Skyborne%20flight%20instructor%20who%20spent%20a%20decade%20in%20the%20Royal%20Navy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20collage%20of%20the%20exterior%20and%20first-person%20view%20of%20a%20Diamond%20DA42%20flight%20simulator%20at%20Skyborne.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66fd4dc97de5c8fd48349372%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20exterior%20and%20interior%20of%20the%20Diamond%20DA42%20flight%20simulator.%3Cp%3EPete%20Syme%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGetting%20to%20grips%20with%20the%20basics%20was%20relatively%20simple%3A%20left%20hand%20on%20the%20stick%2C%20right%20hand%20on%20the%20thrust%20levers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20Gloucestershire%20Airport%20runway%20projected%20in%20front%20of%20us%2C%20takeoff%20went%20smoothly%20%E2%80%94%20largely%20thanks%20to%20Yemm%20guiding%20me%20through%20the%20throttle%20and%20helping%20keep%20the%20jet%20on%20the%20centerline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20strange%20feeling%20guiding%20the%20stick%20with%20my%20left%20hand%20as%20I%20practiced%20some%20sharp%20turns.%20At%20one%20point%2C%20the%20steep%20angle%20triggered%20an%20alert%20%E2%80%94%20but%20not%20to%20the%20extent%20that%20I%20lost%20control.%20If%20it%20were%20a%20real%20plane%2C%20I%20probably%20would've%20panicked%20hearing%20that%20beep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b96cfc77-a8a4-4c3b-8830-2d2d817e1c74%5C%22%3EFlying%20the%20737%20Max%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20more%20imposing%20simulator%20was%20that%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboeing-737-max-safety-record-crashes-issues-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBoeing%20737%20Max%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20proved%20harder%20than%20I%20imagined%2C%20even%20with%20an%20expert%20pilot%20by%20my%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENick%20Heard%2C%20Skyborne's%20manager%20of%20multi-pilot%20training%2C%20spent%2016%20years%20in%20the%20UK's%20Royal%20Air%20Force%20followed%20by%2017%20years%20flying%20Boeing%20747s%20with%20Cathay%20Pacific.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20classroom%2C%20the%20simulator%20was%20large%2C%20gray%2C%20and%20peculiarly%20shaped%3A%20imagine%20half%20a%20sphere%20stuck%20to%20the%20back%20of%20a%20portacabin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20once%20I%20was%20in%20the%20captain's%20seat%2C%20it%20felt%20just%20like%20the%20real%20thing%3A%20a%20flight%20deck%20with%20sheepskin-covered%20seats%20and%20myriad%20switches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20exterior%20of%20a%20Boeing%20737%20Max%20simulator%20in%20a%20classroom%20at%20Skyborne%20pilot%20training%20academy%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66fd505b9e0c5c2eeee9f804%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20entrance%20to%20the%20Boeing%20737%20Max%20simulator.%3Cp%3EPete%20Syme%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThankfully%2C%20I%20didn't%20need%20to%20learn%20what%20%3Cem%3Eall%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethe%20bells%20and%20whistles%20did.%20At%20first%20it%20seemed%20simple%2C%20but%20only%20because%20we%20were%20flying%20with%20autopilot%20during%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHeard%20would%20read%20out%20a%20heading%20%E2%80%94%20the%20compass%20direction%20for%20the%20plane%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I%20only%20needed%20to%20turn%20a%20knob%20to%20let%20the%20computer%20direct%20it%20accordingly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20communication%20gave%20me%20a%20taste%20of%20how%20Skyborne%20utilizes%20the%20737%20Max%20simulator%20for%20cadets%20to%20learn%20how%20to%20work%20with%20others%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Airline%20Pilot%20Standards%20Multi-Crew%20Cooperation%20Course%20(APS%20MCC).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAutopilot%20can%20do%20almost%20everything%2C%20but%20it's%20enthralling%20to%20experience%20the%20magic%20yourself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20with%20control%20in%20my%20hands%2C%20I%20started%20to%20get%20confused.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHeard%20had%20me%20pay%20attention%20to%20the%20flight%20deck%20instruments.%20The%20flight%20director%2C%20a%20pink%20cross%2C%20showed%20me%20where%20I%20needed%20to%20direct%20the%20plane%20%E2%80%94%20represented%20by%20a%20black%20dot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20first-person%20view%20from%20the%20flight%20deck%20of%20a%20Boeing%20737%20Max%20simulator%20during%20a%20sharp%20turn%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66fd51669e0c5c2eeee9f882%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20pilot's%20perspective%20during%20a%20turn.%3Cp%3EPete%20Syme%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20soon%20got%20mixed%20up%2C%20forgetting%20which%20graphic%20I%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20directing%20and%20which%20one%20I%20was%20following.%20In%20my%20haze%2C%20it%20was%20as%20if%20I%20was%20playing%20a%20video%20game%20with%20the%20inverted%20controls%20setting%20mistakenly%20activated.%20I%20felt%20myself%20sweating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20asked%20Heard%20to%20remind%20me%20how%20I%20was%20supposed%20to%20follow%20the%20screen%20and%20soon%20found%20myself%20back%20on%20course.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20without%20my%20confusion%2C%20it%20wasn't%20easy.%20The%20737%20yoke%20wasn't%20as%20mobile%20as%20the%20DA42's%20stick.%20I%20found%20it%20required%20a%20bit%20of%20effort%20to%20move%2C%20but%20the%20motions%20could%20then%20be%20quite%20sudden.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20I%20got%20the%20hang%20of%20it%2C%20Heard%20changed%20the%20simulator%20settings%20to%20nighttime.%20The%20English%20countryside%20below%20was%20replaced%20by