20during%20the%20night%2C%20Heard's%20words%20helped%20me%20comprehend%20the%20difficulty%20of%20being%20an%20airline%20pilot.%20He%20explained%20how%20this%20is%20what%20much%20of%20the%20day-to-day%20job%20can%20be%20like%20%E2%80%94%20coupled%20with%20jet%20lag%20and%20a%20lack%20of%20sleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20fun%2C%20but%20I'd%20certainly%20struggle%20with%20changing%20time%20zones%20as%20frequently%20as%20an%20airline%20pilot%2C%20let%20alone%20going%20through%2018%20months%20of%20training%20and%20perfecting%20how%20to%20control%20an%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboeing-737-max-simulator-what-its-like-to-be-pilot-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728123782000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66fc03ea75c877a99b621f5f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboeing-737-max-simulator-what-its-like-to-be-pilot-2024-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Business%20Insider's%20author%20tried%20two%20flight%20simulators%20at%20Skyborne%2C%20a%20pilot%20training%20academy%2C%20and%20attempted%20an%20ultra-low-visibility%20landing.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22psyme%40businessinsider.com%20(Pete%20Syme)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboeing-737-max-simulator-what-its-like-to-be-pilot-2024-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%224%20market%20experts%20share%2010%20places%20to%20invest%20your%20money%20after%20September's%20jobs%20data%20blew%20expectations%20out%20of%20the%20water%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221868%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Worker%20standing%20in%20workshop%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66fd986f7de5c8fd4834c2ca%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221246%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAme