Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20decided%20to%20pivot%20into%20tech.%20It%20was%20a%20natural%20transition%20for%20Sadler%2C%20who%20had%20experience%20working%20on%20websites%20for%20the%20smaller%20food%20businesses%20she'd%20worked%20at.%20In%202021%2C%20she%20landed%20her%20first%20job%20as%20a%20UI%2FUX%20designer.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20lasted%20in%20tech%20for%20nearly%20four%20years.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BI%20unfortunately%20did%20get%20laid%20off%20in%202022%20from%20the%20company%20I%20was%20working%20at%20and%20then%20I%20got%20laid%20off%20in%202024%20again.%20I%20realized%20that%20kind%20of%20a%20similar%20thing%20was%20happening%20in%20tech%20that%20had%20previously%20happened%20with%20the%20food%20industry%20during%20Covid%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sadler.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bab6316a-f4b4-4657-8e04-eff019b6ee66%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EFrom%20tech%20to%20small%20business%3A%20Taking%20a%20pay%20cut%20but%20gaining%20more%20control%20and%20freedom%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20the%20second%20tech%20layoff%20in%202024%2C%20Sadler%20reevaluated%20her%20situation%2C%20much%20like%20she%20did%20in%202020%2C%20and%20felt%20like%20it%20was%20as%20good%20a%20time%20as%20any%20to%20go%20all-in%20on%20her%20side%20hustle%3A%20making%20custom%20pet%20portraits%20and%20accessories%20like%20keychains%20and%20pet%20tags%2C%20which%20she'd%20been%20doing%20since%202023.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20side%20project%20served%20two%20purposes%3A%20It%20provided%20extra%20income%20that%20she%20could%20draw%20on%20if%20she%20lost%20her%20job%20and%20provided%20a%20creative%20outlet%20for%20someone%20who%20grew%20up%20making%20art.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BTech%20is%20very%20screen%20heavy.%20It's%20a%20different%20type%20of%20creativity%2C%20and%20I've%20always%20been%20a%20very%20tactile%20artist%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20really%20wanted%20another%20outlet%20where%20I%20could%20make%20something%20physical%20and%20not%20just%20something%20digital.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22emma%20sadler%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67004c74198738e3a70e7519%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESadler%20says%20her%20drawings%20stem%20from%20her%20'ink%20and%20paper'%20art%20style.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Emma%20Sadler%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20settled%20on%20custom%20pet%20accessories%20because%20it%20was%20something%20she%20personally%20wanted%20but%20couldn't%20easily%20find.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20what's%20out%20there%20for%20keychains%20or%20magnets%20or%20portraits%20are%20all%20based%20around%20designs%20because%20they're%20more%20scalable%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sadler.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I%20had%20mutts.%20They're%20unique.%20They%20have%20their%20own%20personalities.%20And%20so%20that's%20kind%20of%20how%20it%20started%3A%20I%20want%20a%20keychain%20of%20my%20dog%2C%20but%20none%20of%20these%20really%20look%20like%20my%20dog.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20test%20whether%20other%20people%20also%20wanted%20custom%20pet%20portraits%20and%20accessories%2C%20Sadler%20applied%20for%20a%20pop-up%20event%20in%20Brooklyn%20so%20she%20could%20interact%20with%20customers%20and%20get%20feedback.%20She%20continued%20doing%20in-person%20events%20around%20New%20York%20and%20started%20profiting%20after%20the%202023%20holiday%20season%2C%20which%20confirmed%20that%20she%20was%20onto%20something.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBy%20the%20time%20she%20was%20let%20go%20from%20her%20day%20job%20in%20early%202024%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20like%2C%20it's%20now%20or%20never.%20I%20have%20these%20skills%2C%20I've%20been%20building%20this%20business%2C%20people%20are%20inte