ere's%20a%20lot%20of%20small%20businesses%20that%20can%20take%20a%20very%2C%20very%20long%20time%2C%20especially%20for%20something%20that's%20custom.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22emma%20sadler%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67004cd8198738e3a70e759a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESadler%20makes%20ornaments%2C%20keychains%2C%20apparel%2C%20and%20totes.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Emma%20Sadler%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHer%20monthly%20income%20hasn't%20come%20close%20to%20surpassing%20what%20she%20was%20earning%20in%20tech%2C%20and%20she%20does%20some%20freelance%20work%20as%20an%20email%20marketing%20designer%20and%20presentation%20designer%2C%20she%20noted%3A%20%26quot%3BDo%20I%20think%20it%20could%20eventually%20one%20day%20get%20to%20pay%20my%20salary%3F%20Yes.%20But%20as%20of%20right%20now%2C%20in%20the%20first%20year%2C%20it's%20definitely%20not%20comparable%20with%20that%2C%20which%20is%20why%20I%20do%20have%20some%20part-time%20jobs%20to%20help%20supplement%20because%20I%20do%20want%20to%20put%20as%20much%20of%20it%20back%20into%20the%20business.%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20really%20pay%20myself%20right%20now%20if%20I%20can%20avoid%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20meantime%2C%20she%20has%20peace%20of%20mind%20knowing%20that%20her%20earnings%20are%20broadly%20in%20her%20control.%20She%20expects%20fluctuations%20%E2%80%94%20the%20end-of-year%20holiday%20season%20is%20much%20busier%20than%20January%20and%20February%2C%20for%20example%20%E2%80%94%20but%20she%20doesn't%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20layoffs%20and%20her%20income%20abruptly%20halting.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BBuilding%20something%20that's%20your%20own%20definitely%20comes%20with%20a%20certain%20level%20of%20contentment%20%E2%80%94%20knowing%20that%20it's%20something%2C%20to%20a%