%20expanding%20the%20small%20business%20tax%20credit%20from%20%245%2C000%20to%20%2450%2C000.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EExperts%20told%20BI%20the%20proposal%20would%20shift%20the%20timing%20of%20deductions%20and%20isn't%20all%20that%20pricey.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIf%20the%20proposal%20inspired%20more%20small%20business%20creation%2C%20it%20would%20likely%20spur%20economic%20growth.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EPatricia%20Oswlad%2C%2055%2C%20and%20her%20husband%20have%20spent%20years%20building%20up%20their%20retirement%20fund.%20But%20when%20Oswald%20decided%20to%20launch%20a%20small%20business%20in%20the%20fall%20of%202022%2C%20the%20couple%20liquidated%20some%20of%20their%20assets%20to%20fund%20the%20company%2C%20throwing%20their%20financial%20planning%20to%20the%20wind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20fewer%20than%20five%20weeks%20until%20Election%20Day%2C%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkamala-harris-small-businesses-tax-breaks-cut-red-tape-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emaking%20a%20targeted%20pitch%20to%20entrepreneurs%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20Oswald%2C%20who%20are%20burdened%20by%20startup%20expenses.%20She%20even%20mentioned%20a%20key%20proposal%20in%20her%20opening%20answer%20at%20the%20presidential%20debate%3A%20expand%20the%20small%20business%20tax%20credit%2010-fold%2C%20from%20%245%2C000%20to%20%2450%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20pamphlet%20on%20her%20economic%20plan%2C%20dubbed%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-you-need-to-know-about-kamala-harris-opportunity-economy-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BOpportunity%20Economy%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20Harris%20explains%20that%20she%20would%20let%20business%20owners%20take%20advantage%20of%20the%20%2450%2C000%20tax%20deduction%20right%20away%20or%20a%20few%20years%20after%20launching%2C%20to%20help%20lower%20taxes%20once%20they%20start%20turning%20a%20profit.%20The%20proposal%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fharris-added-policy-website-before-trump-debate-venture-capital-startups-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elike%20many%20of%20her%20others%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20would%20need%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkamala-harris-senate-races-ted-cruz-rick-scott-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econgressional%3C%2Fa%3E%20approval.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOswald%20told%20Business%20Insider%20the%20credit%20would%20have%20been%20%26quot%3Binvaluable%26quot%3B%20in%20getting%20Brisa%20Systems%2C%20which%20offers%20powered%20drying%20racks%2C%20off%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227006e4c2-613d-4eb9-8fc4-ad020faacaad%5C%22%3EHarris'%20proposal%20shifts%20the%20tax%20timeline%20for%20entrepreneurs.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETax%20experts%20told%20BI%20that%20enacting%20the%20credit%20would%20mean%20a%20change%20in%20timing%20more%20than%20anything%20else.%20Under%20current%20law%2C%20small%20businesses%20can%20deduct%20up%20to%20%245%2C000%20in%20expenses%20immediately%20and%20must%20deduct%20any%20future%20expenses%20against%20their%20income%20over%2015%20years.%20Harris'%20proposal%20would%20let%20entrepreneurs%20deduct%20more%20money%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOwners%20have%20expenses%20before%20even%20launching%20their%20business%2C%20and%20the%20deduction%20would%20help%20cover%20those%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERhett%20Buttle%2C%20the%20co-executive%20director%20of%20Small%20Business%20Roundtable%20and%20a%20former%20business%20advisor%20for%20President%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20startup%20costs%20accumulate%20in%20three%20primary%20areas%3A%20marketing%2C%20basic%20equipment%2C%20and%20hiring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Oswald%2C%20most%20early%20costs%20have%20been%20in%20manufacturing%20and%20intellectual%20property%20services.%20Taylor%20McCleneghan%2C%20who%20launched%20her%20product%20development%20company%2C%20Small%20Shop%20LLC%2C%20in%202018%2C%20named%20inventory%20and%20marketing%20as%20the%20biggest%20upfront%20costs.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBoth%20women%20are%20based%20in%20the%20Chicago%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225159%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kamala%20Harris%20at%20a%20campaign%20event%20about%20small%20businesses%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67000ebfa7031864927f801a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223439%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHarris%20has%20made%20supporting%20small%20business%20a%20key%20part%20of%20her%20economic%20agenda.%3Cp%3EDanielle%20Parhizkaran%2FThe%20Boston%20Globe%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBrett%20Theodos%2C%20a%20senior%20fellow%20at%20Urban%20Institute%20who%20specializes%20in%20small%20business%20loans%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20entrepreneurs%20would%20%26quot%3Blove%26quot%3B%20to%20be%20able%20to%20deduct%20more%20of%20those%20expenses%20right%20away.%20Moving%20up%20the%20timeline%20would%2C%20he%20said%2C%20make%20many%20feel%20less%20strapped%20for%20cash%20from%20the%20very%20outset.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20there's%20another%20potential%20upside%2C%20according%20to%20Garret%20Watson%2C%20a%20senior%20policy%20analyst%20at%20the%20nonpartisan%20Tax%20Foundation.%20Small%20businesses%20would%20likely%20benefit%20from%20getting%20the%20deduction%20more%20quickly%20because%20of%20inflation%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20entrepreneurs%20are%20psyched%20about%20the%20effort.%20Theodos%20struggled%20to%20think%20of%20a%20reason%20why%20they%20wouldn't%20want%20this%2C%20and%20Buttle%20said%20that%20those%20he%20works%20with%20are%20overwhelmingly%20excited%20about%20the%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcCleneghan%2C%20of%20the%20Small%20Shop%2C%20said%20having%20access%20to%20a%20%2450%2C000%20tax%20deduction%20early%20on%20would%20have%20allowed%20her%20to%20do%20better%20long-term%20planning.%20With%20the%20expanded%20tax%20deduction%2C%20Oswald%20said%20she%20might%20not%20have%20had%20to%20divest%20retirement%20funds%20or%20take%20out%20lines%20of%20credit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGetting%20money%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20entrepreneurs%20sooner%20is%20going%20to%20allow%20them%20to%20hire%2C%20to%20get%20equipment%2C%20to%20get%20a%20space%2C%20to%20pay%20off%20some%20debt%2C%20to%20pay%20themselves%2C%26quot%3B%20Theodos%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20it's%20meaningful%20to%20allow%20them%20to%20accelerate%20the%20deduction%20of%20startup%20expenses.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20while%20small%20business%20owners%20may%20jump%20at%20the%20opportunity%20for%20more%20early%20cash%20flow%2C%20where%20this%20money%20would%20come%20from%20is%20more%20unclear.%20McCleneghan%20herself%20acknowledged%20that%20the%20details%20seem%20hazy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22af50011b-34e9-4f5e-9a3b-b001ea7f148b%5C%22%3EDespite%20the%20flashy%20numbers%2C%20the%20proposal%20likely%20wouldn't%20have%20a%20significant%20impact%20on%20the%20federal%20budget.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20%2450%2C000%20sounds%20like%20a%20big-ticket%20promise%2C%20the%20experts%20BI%20spoke%20to%20said%20Harris'%20proposal%20actually%20wouldn't%20make%20a%20big%20dent%20in%20the%20federal%20budget.%20The%20Tax%20Foundation%2C%20where%20Watson%20works%2C%20examined%20cost%20estimates%20from%20prior%20expansions%20and%20found%20that%20the%20proposal%20would%20cost%20about%20%2424.5%20billion%20over%2010%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRelative%20to%20the%20federal%20government's%20budget%20and%20spending%2C%20it's%20very%20small%2C%26quot%3B%20Watson%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20%2425%20billion%20number%20is%20in%20the%20context%20of%20a%20tax%20plan%20for%20the%20Harris%20campaign%20that%20would%20raise%20about%20%245%20trillion%20over%2010%20years.%20So%20you're%20talking%20about%20orders%20of%20magnitude%20more%20money%20on%20the%20tax%20hike%20side.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kamala%20Harris%20and%20Mike%20Johnson%20during%20the%20State%20of%20the%20Union%20speech%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F670010613f2165d716de7c15%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHarris'%20proposal%20would%20require%20congressional%20approval.%3Cp%3EChip%20Somodevilla%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20loss%2C%20he%20said%2C%20stems%20from%20the%20likelihood%20that%20certain%20entrepreneurs%20will%20use%20the%20deduction%20and%20then%20go%20out%20of%20business.%20Since%20the%20proposal%20changes%20when%20businesses%20can%20deduct%20rather%20than%20how%20much%20they%20deduct%2C%20it%20will%20cost%20some%20money%2C%20but%20not%20%26quot%3Bbig%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20Theodos%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20proposal%20could%20help%20spur%20growth%2C%20if%20it%20becomes%20law.%20According%20to%20a%20study%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pewresearch.org%2Fshort-reads%2F2024%2F04%2F22%2Fa-look-at-small-businesses-in-the-us%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPew%20Research%20Center%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20in%20April%202024%2C%20small%20businesses%20employ%20nearly%20half%20of%20the%20country's%20private%20sector%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheodos%20called%20small%20businesses%20%26quot%3Bessential%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20US%20economy%2C%20and%20Buttle%20said%20they're%20a%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fharris-sec-ftc-khan-gensler-crypto-regulation-biden-warren-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20crucial%20source%20of%20innovation%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20the%20tax%20experts%20said%20the%20full%20potential%20economic%20impact%20of%20the%20proposed%20expansion%20is%20still%20up%20in%20the%20air.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20question%20is%2C%20will%20this%20significantly%20contribute%20to%20a%20startup%20boom%20or%20really%20change%20the%20needle%20there%20or%20move%20the%20needle%20there%3F%20I%20think%20that's%20a%20reasonable%20question.%20It's%20up%20for%20debate%2C%20particularly%20because%20this%20is%20such%20a%20narrow%20provision%2C%26quot%3B%20Watson%20told%20BI%2C%20while%20noting%20that%20giving%20businesses%20deductions%20is%20generally%20a%20good%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20policy%20did%20spur%20more%20development%2C%20though%2C%20Mary%20Hansen%2C%20an%20economics%20professor%20at%20American%20University%20and%20co-director%20of%20the%20nonpartisan%20Institute%20for%20Macroeconomic%20and%20Policy%20Analysis%2C%20said%20it%20would%20eventually%20have%20a%20net%20positive%20impact%20on%20government%20revenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20now%2C%20Harris'%20promise%20is%20just%20that%20%E2%80%94%20a%20promise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShould%20she%20win%20the%20election%2C%20Congress%20would%20need%20to%20pass%20legislation%20to%20turn%20her%20expanded%20tax%20deduction%20idea%20into%20a%20reality.%20Despite%20the%20prevailing%20congressional%20gridlock%2C%20all%20of%20the%20experts%20BI%20spoke%20with%20said%20small%20businesses%20are%20a%20rare%20point%20of%20potential%20bipartisan%20agreement.%20Watson%20predicted%20that%20lawmakers%20would%20likely%20tie%20the%20proposal%20to%20their%20actions%20on%20the%20expiring%202017%20tax%20provisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225973%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kamala%20Harris%20and%20Doug%20Emhoff%20go%20shopping%20to%20support%20Small%20Business%20Saturday%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67000f4ca7031864927f806c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223788%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHarris'%20proposal%20would%20disproportionately%20impact%20entrepreneurs%20with%20less%20access%20to%20capital%2C%20namely%20women%20and%20people%20of%20color.%3Cp%3EFrancine%20Orr%20%2F%20Los%20Angeles%20Times%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EShould%20Congress%20ever%20pass%20the%20expanded%20tax%20deduction%2C%20all%20startups%20and%20small%20businesses%20would%20access%20the%20same%20amount%20of%20money%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20experts%20told%20BI%20that%20some%20would%20feel%20the%20impact%20more%20than%20others.%20Entrepreneurs%20with%20less%20initial%20cash%20flow%20would%20disproportionately%20benefit%20from%20the%20change%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EButtle%20said%20it%20would%20help%20women%20and%20people%20of%20color%20who%20have%20a%20harder%20time%20accessing%20capital.%20The%20Pew%20Research%20study%20found%2061%25%20of%20small%20businesses%20are%20majority-owned%20by%20men%20and%2C%20as%20of%202021%2C%2085%25%20were%20majority-white%20owned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20talking%20about%20community%20businesses%2C%20micro-businesses%2C%20businesses%20where%20the%20founder%20doesn't%20have%20as%20much%20net%20worth%2C%26quot%3B%20Theodos%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BEverybody%20can%20benefit%20from%20%2445%2C000%2C%20but%20the%20question%20is%2C%20who%20is%20that%20making%20the%20critical%20difference%20for%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fharris-tax-deduction-plan-small-business-startup-cost-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728120961000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66feba5a9e0c5c2eeeea5d9a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fharris-tax-deduction-plan-small-business-startup-cost-2024-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20proposal%20may%20represent%20an%20opportunity%20for%20bipartisan%20agreement%2C%20as%20experts%20told%20BI%20that%20neither%20party%20benefits%20from%20seeming%20anti-small%20business.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22atecotzky%40businessinsider.com%20(Alice%20Tecotzky)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fharris-tax-deduction-plan-small-business-startup-cost-2024-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20Swiss%20town%2