ollar%20donors%20to%20campaigns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20Barack%20Obama's%202012%20reelection%20campaign%20is%20seen%20as%20the%20pioneer%20of%20the%20urgent%20fundraising%20appeal.%20One%20email%20simply%20entitled%20%26quot%3BI%20will%20be%20outspent%26quot%3B%20generated%20more%20than%20%242.6%20million%20that%20year%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2012-11-29%2Fthe-science-behind-those-obama-campaign-e-mails%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20Bloomberg%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20over%20time%2C%20some%20campaigns%20have%20taken%20an%20increasingly%20apocalyptic%20tone%2C%20employing%20increasingly%20guilt-driven%20tactics.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20we're%20at%20a%20point%20where%20a%20campaign%20may%20tell%20you%20the%20fate%20of%20the%20election%2C%20and%20the%20country%2C%20depends%20on%20your%20%2420.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.twitter.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22twitter%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20going%20to%20be%20deleted!%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EBig%20Tech%20is%20about%20to%20delete%20Ted%20Cruz%E2%80%99s%20message%20in%207%20minutes!%20Watch%20it%20below%20before%20it%E2%80%99s%20too%20late%20%3E%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Senate%20Republicans%20(%40NRSC)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNRSC%2Fstatus%2F1800883352196505744%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJune%2012%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFormer%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20campaign%20has%20embraced%20this%20strategy.%20It%20has%20sent%20emails%20ranging%20from%20%26quot%3BBiden's%20political%20firing%20squad%20is%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpoliticalemails.org%2Fmessages%2F1454419%2527%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Elining%20up%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3B%20to%20more%20banal%20gimmicks%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpoliticalemails.org%2Fmessages%2F1582554%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elike%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%26quot%3Bthe%20most%20important%20email%20I've%20ever%20sent.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJust%20this%20week%2C%20those%20on%20the%20campaign's%20distribution%20list%20received%20one%20that%20read%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpoliticalemails.org%2Fmessages%2F1579224%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%26quot%3Ball%20hell%20breaks%20loose%20at%2011%3A59%20PM!%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20key%20factor%20here%20is%20message%20testing%2C%20%3Cspan%3Ecampaign%20operatives%20told%20BI%3C%2Fspan%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPolitical%20campaigns%20and%20the%20professional%20firms%20they%20hire%20to%20implement%20their%20fundraising%20strategies%20get%20real-time%20data%20about%20which%20messages%20raise%20lots%20of%20money%20and%20which%20ones%20don't%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20able%20to%20rapidly%20test%20things%2C%20and%20that%20can%20bring%20you%20down%20a%20rabbit%20hole%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Kenneth%20Pennington%2C%20partner%20at%20the%20progressive%20campaign%20firm%20Middle%20Seat.%20%26quot%3BSo%20if%20ratcheting%20up%20the%20desperation%20is%20bringing%20in%20more%20dollars%20than%20versions%20of%20the%20content%20that%20have%20less%20desperation%2C%20it%20might%20lead%20you%20to%20believe%20that%20more%20desperation%20is%20always%20good.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20an%20arms-race%20dynamic%20to%20it%20all.%20Just%20about%20everyone%20%E2%80%94%20from%20presidential%20candidates%20to%20city%20council%20hopefuls%20%E2%80%94%20is%20fundraising%20via%20email%2C%20texts%2C%20and%20social%20media.%20Campaigns%20are%20forced%20to%20compete%20over%20a%20limited%20amount%20of%20people's%20attention%20and%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20race%20to%20the%20bottom%20to%20get%20attention%2C%20and%20that%20makes%20people%20increasingly%20desperate%2C%26quot%3B%20Nellis%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20make%20some%20choices%2C%26quot%3B%20Pennington%20said.%20%26quot%3BEither%20I'm%20going%20to%20send%20out%20a%20lot%20more%20messages%20to%20compete%20with%20the%20volume%20of%20messages%20that%20are%20already%20out%20there%2C%20or%20I'm%20going%20to%20ratchet%20up%20the%20nature%20of%20those%20messages%2C%20make%20them%20more%20desperate%2C%20or%20more%20alarming%2C%20or%20eye-catching%20or%20urgent.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c3850a0f-b585-4fc2-9520-09a4777bf411%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Ways%20to%20get%20attention%20that%20I%20think%20you%20wouldn't%20be%20super%20proud%20of'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20were%20hoping%20that%20the%20volume%20and%20urgency%20of%20political%20fundraising%20messages%20might%20ever%20truly%20diminish%2C%20you're%20out%20of%20luck%20%E2%80%94%20the%20only%20way%20to%20change%20that%20would%20be%20to%20decrease%20the%20importance%20of%20money%20in%20politics%20via%20campaign%20finance%20reform%2C%20and%20that%20seems%20more%20illusory%20than%20ever%2C%20the%20operatives%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20meantime%2C%20campaigns%20aren't%20going%20to%20unilaterally%20disarm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20really%20have%20a%20moral%20problem%20with%20sending%20a%20lot%20of%20emails%20to%20you%20to%20elect%20another%20Democratic%20senator%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Pennington.%20%26quot%3BCampaigning%20is%20a%20big%20part%20of%20American%20life%2C%20and%20if%20we%20want%20to%20change%20it%2C%20we%20should%20change%20some%20of%20our%20laws.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there's%20a%20big%2C%20ongoing%20internal%20conversation%20among%20campaign%20professionals%20in%20both%20parties%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F50-professionals-urge-democratic-fundraising-company-crackdown-spam-deceptive-emails-2021-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehow%20far%20is%20too%20far%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20how%20to%20avoid%20the%20long-term%20consequences%20of%20scorched-earth%20fundraising%20appeals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20ways%20to%20go%20after%20and%20get%20attention%20that%20I%20think%20you%20can%20hold%20your%20head%20up%20high%20and%20feel%20pretty%20good%20about%20that%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20Nellis%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20there%20are%20ways%20to%20get%20attention%20that%20I%20think%20you%20wouldn't%20be%20super%20proud%20of%2C%20like%20sending%20out%20emails%20that%20are%20like%20'the%20sky%20is%20falling%2C%20we're%20all%20gonna%20die%20if%20you%20don't%20donate%20%2410.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20growing%20number%20of%20campaigns%20are%20now%20drawing%20the%20line%20at%20engaging%20in%20tactics%20that%20are%20outright%20scammy%2C%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcampaign-matching-donations-democrats-republicans-bogus-gimmick-2021-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eclaiming%20that%20donations%20will%20be%20matched%3C%2Fa%3E%20multiple%20times%20over%20when%20that's%20not%20the%20case%2C%20or%20roping%20people%20into%20making%20recurring%20donations%20without%20them%20being%20fully%20aware%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOthers%20are%20simply%20pushing%20for%20more%20honesty%20%E2%80%94%20being%20realistic%20about%20what%20an%20individual%20donor's%20contribution%20will%20mean%20for%20the%20campaign%20while%20avoiding%20manipulating%20people's%20emotions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohn%20Hall%2C%20a%20leading%20GOP%20fundraising%20and%20communications%20professional%2C%20called%20for%20honesty%20with%20donors%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40john_13136%2Fmy-principles-for-online-fundraising-8dea4595ae6f%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMedium%20post%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20year%2C%20arguing%20failing%20to%20uphold%20that%20principle%20would%20eventually%20lead%20to%20donor%20burnout.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20raises%20the%20most%20money%20is%20often%20the%20most%20extreme%20messaging%2C%20the%20most%20aggressive%20tactics%2C%20and%20a%20willingness%20to%20guilt%20individuals%20into%20donating%2C%26quot%3B%20Hall%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BThis%20tactic%20is%20effective%20at%20getting%20an%20immediate%20initial%20donation%2C%20but%20over%20time%2C%20the%20donor%20is%20either%20desensitized%20to%20or%20begins%20to%20resent%20this%20'strategy.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDonor%20burnout%20has%20become%20a%20real%20problem%20for%20Republicans%2C%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fpolitics%2F2024%2F04%2F01%2Ftrump-republican-small-donations-problems%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Washington%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20in%20April.%20Trump%20and%20the%20RNC%20have%20brought%20in%20less%20money%20from%20smaller%20donors%20than%20expected%20compared%20to%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it's%20a%20difficult%20problem%20to%20address%20as%20a%20party%2C%20or%20as%20an%20industry%2C%20in%20part%20due%20to%20the%20structure%20of%20campaigns%20themselves.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20crop%20up%20when%20a%20candidate%20runs%20for%20office%20and%20often%20disappear%20when%20they%20lose%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20long-term%20thinking%20about%20the%20effect%20their%20appeals%20have%20on%20the%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20way%20to%20avoid%20sounding%20too%20embarrassing%20and%20veering%20into%20manipulative%20tactics%2C%20campaign%20operatives%20argue%2C%20is%20to%20simply%20lean%20into%20the%20talents%20that%20a%20politician%20already%20has.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20candidate%20is%20inspiring%20to%20voters%20on%20their%20own%2C%20there's%20less%20need%20to%20scare%20people%20into%20sending%20them%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris%2C%20for%20example%2C%20has%20raised%20record-shattering