20the%20Walmart%2C%20so%20she%20ventured%20to%20the%20store%20to%20call%20her%20parents%20in%20Illinois%20and%20give%20them%20an%20update.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20a%20crowd%20of%20about%20100%2C%20200%20students%20sitting%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20Walmart%20in%20the%20tech%20department%20trying%20to%20call%20our%20parents%2C%26quot%3B%20Nelson%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20She%20said%20she%20called%20her%20mom%20from%20someone%20else's%20phone%20because%20she%20didn't%20yet%20have%20service%20on%20hers.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20trying%20to%20contact%20anyone%20I%20could%20just%20so%20I%20could%20make%20sure%20they%20knew%20I%20was%20OK%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENelson%20was%20among%20thousands%20of%20college%20students%20across%20North%20Carolina%20who%20experienced%20disruptions%2C%20including%20class%20cancellations%20through%20at%20least%20the%20end%20of%20October.%20While%20some%20managed%20to%20leave%20campus%20and%20go%20home%2C%20Nelson%20wasn't%20able%20to%20make%20it%20back%20to%20Illinois.%20She%20waited%20on%20the%20WCU%20campus%20to%20learn%20what%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20semester%20would%20look%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22589%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Abby%20Nelson%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6700424aa7031864927f9bae%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22442%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAbby%20Nelson%2C%20a%20WCU%20student%2C%20had%20to%20huddle%20in%20a%20Walmart%20to%20call%20her%20parents%20after%20Hurricane%20Helene%20hit.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Abby%20Nelson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20impact%20of%20Helene%20has%20been%20devastating.%20At%20least%20215%20have%20died%2C%20hundreds%20are%20missing%2C%20and%20over%20half%20of%20the%20deaths%20were%20in%20North%20Carolina.%20Nelson%20said%20she%20never%20could%20have%20anticipated%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20hurricane.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20close%20peers%20who%20had%20family%20who%20lost%20power%20and%20service%2C%20and%20I%20have%20a%20friend%20whose%20house%20was%20entirely%20gone%20by%20that%20flood%20a%20couple%20hours%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20Nelson%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20there%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20pain%20and%20anxiety%20in%20the%20community%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20college%20over%20this%20past%20weekend%20from%20Saturday%20to%20Sunday%20as%20well%2C%20as%20we%20found%20out%20what%20was%20happening%20around%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWNC%2C%20the%20University%20of%20North%20Carolina%20Asheville%2C%20and%20other%20colleges%20in%20the%20state%20have%20canceled%20classes%20until%20the%20end%20of%20October%20as%20they%20work%20to%20repair%20damage%20on%20campus%20and%20restore%20power%20and%20water.%20College%20students%20impacted%20by%20the%20hurricane%20told%20BI%20that%20while%20their%20communities%20have%20banded%20together%20to%20help%20those%20in%20need%2C%20they're%20also%20left%20in%20limbo%20regarding%20their%20classes%2C%20finances%2C%20and%20plans%20for%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEntire%20towns%20are%20destroyed%2C%20and%20there's%20so%20much%20flooding%20and%20so%20much%20hurt%2C%20it's%20a%20lot%20to%20take%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20Nelson%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20been%20a%20hard%20part%2C%20as%20well%2C%20about%20being%20in%20college%20here%20because%20I'm%20just%20not%20used%20to%20the%20hurricanes%20around%20any%20of%20these%20states.%20So%20it's%20just%20been%20a%20lot%20of%20anxiety%20and%20unsureness%20about%20that%2C%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ac0b0d23-d526-4af5-99a7-32af81cea2d5%5C%22%3E'You%20don't%20realize%20how%20many%20things%20you%20think%20about%20once%20you've%20been%20displaced'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAsa%20Hoffman%20and%20Ashley%20Wahlers%2C%20both%2021%2C%20are%20seniors%20at%20UNC%20Asheville%2C%20where%20classes%20are%20canceled%20until%20October%2028.%20Having%20grown%20up%20in%20central%20North%20Carolina%2C%20Hoffman%20said%20he%20was%20used%20to%20hurricane%20season%20and%20didn't%20think%20Asheville%20would%20be%20too%20severely%20impacted.%20But%20after%20the%20campus%20lost%20power%2C%20water%2C%20and%20any%20contact%20with%20family%20members%20off%20campus%2C%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20hurricane%20began%20to%20set%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHoffman%20and%20his%20girlfriend%20Wahlers%20left%20campus%20on%20September%2028%20to%20stay%20at%20his%20home%20in%20Chapel%20Hill.%20Wahlers%20said%20that%20she%20waited%20in%20line%20at%20the%20gas%20station%20for%20three%20hours%2C%20and%20she%20realized%20that%20the%20card%20readers%20weren't%20working%20and%20she%20didn't%20have%20any%20cash%2C%20so%20a%20woman%20at%20the%20station%20filled%20up%20the%20tank%20for%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Hoffman%20and%20Wahlers%20have%20received%20periodic%20communications%20from%20the%20university%20on%20the%20next%20steps%2C%20they%20didn't%20realize%20how%20disruptive%20the%20hurricane%20had%20been%20until%20they%20left%20campus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20first%20got%20back%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20it%20is%20just%20figuring%20things%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20Hoffman%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20realize%20how%20many%20things%20you%20think%20about%20once%20you've%20been%20displaced.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ashley%20Wahlers%20and%20Asa%20Hoffman%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F670042e8a7031864927f9bfa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAshley%20Wahlers%20and%20Asa%20Hoffman%20left%20UNC%20Asheville%20after%20Hurricane%20Helene%20hit%20the%20campus.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Ashley%20Wahlers%20and%20Asa%20Hoffman%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20Hoffman%20said%20he%20was%20supposed%20to%20take%20the%20LSAT%20in%20Asheville%20when%20Hurricane%20Helene%20made%20landfall%2C%20and%20he's%20not%20sure%20when%20he'll%20be%20able%20to%20take%20it%20now.%20And%20with%20his%20job%20being%20based%20in%20Asheville%2C%20he'll%20have%20to%20turn%20to%20alternate%20routes%20to%20make%20money%2C%20including%20working%20for%20DoorDash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENelson%20also%20noted%20that%20the%20situation%20with%20her%20financial%20aid%20is%20uncertain.%20She's%20financing%20her%20education%20largely%20with%20student%20loans%2C%20and%20she's%20not%20sure%20how%20the%20class%20cancellations%20will%20impact%20her%20tuition%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20limbo%20period%20with%20their%20college%20educations%2C%20the%20damage%20in%20their%20communities%20is%20taking%20a%20toll.%20Wahler's%20hometown%20is%20in%20Yancey%20County%2C%20which%20has%20suffered%20severely%20from%20the%20hurricane%2C%20and%20she%20said%20that%20her%20%26quot%3Btown%20is%20destroyed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20so%20sad%20to%20see%20my%20parents'%20neighborhood%20completely%20destroyed%2C%20and%20a%20house%20got%20taken%20away%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20neighborhood.%20And%20my%20sister%2C%20her%20husband's%20nana%2C%20she%20lost%20her%20house%2C%20and%20she%20lost%20everything.%20It's%20just%20awful.%20I%20grew%20up%20here%2C%20and%20that%20is%20my%20home.%20And%20so%20it's%20just%20upsetting.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d7ee4b9b-20da-4347-bc73-757b8d780311%5C%22%3E'This%20is%20something%20that%20we%20had%20to%20get%20through%20on%20our%20own'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAly%20Andrews%2C%2019%2C%20went%20to%20a%20classroom%20on%20WCU's%20campus%20on%20September%2028%20that%20had%20about%2020%20to%2030%20different%20landlines%2C%20and%20she%20stood%20in%20line%20to%20use%20one%20of%20the%20phones%20and%20make%20a%20call%20to%20her%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20day%2C%20she%20sat%20in%20her%20dorm%20room%20and%20searched%20for%20news%20of%20destruction%20in%20the%20areas%20around%20her.%20She%20said%20her%20%26quot%3Bmind%20was%20truly%20blown%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20loss%20of%20property%20and%20lives%