20leads%20the%20Office%20of%20Dietary%20Supplements%20at%20the%20National%20Institutes%20of%20Health%2C%20a%20government%20body%20that%20assesses%20the%20latest%20scientific%20findings%20on%20supplements%20to%20strengthen%20public%20understanding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPasiakos%2C%20a%20nutritional%20scientist%20by%20training%2C%20joined%20the%20ODS%20in%20July%202023%20with%20the%20goal%20of%20bringing%20a%20high%20level%20of%20scientific%20objectivity%20to%20the%20supplement%20field%2C%20he%20said.%20By%20providing%20people%20with%20clear%20information%2C%20he%20hopes%20he%20can%20help%20them%20make%20informed%20choices%20that%20optimize%20their%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDietary%20supplements%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmultivitamins-for-memory-older-adults-benefit-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emultivitamins%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20probiotics%20have%20become%20staples%20in%20our%20bathroom%20cabinets%2C%20with%20almost%2058%25%20of%20Americans%20saying%20they%20had%20taken%20some%20kind%20of%20supplement%20in%20the%20past%2030%20days%2C%20according%20to%20the%20latest%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fnchs%2Fproducts%2Fdatabriefs%2Fdb399.htm%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAmong%2520U.S.%2520adults%2520aged%252020%2C60%2520and%2520over%2520(80.2%2525).%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edata%20from%20the%20CDC%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20in%202021.%20It's%20no%20surprise%2C%20then%2C%20that%20the%20US%20dietary%20supplement%20market%20had%20an%20estimated%20value%20of%20%2445.1%20billion%20in%202023%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.statista.com%2Fstatistics%2F828481%2Ftotal-dietary-supplements-market-size-in-the-us%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStatista%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20FDA%20doesn't%20approve%20supplements%20before%20they%20hit%20the%20market%2C%20meaning%2C%20unlike%20drug%20manufacturers%2C%20companies%20don't%20have%20to%20conduct%20multiple%20clinical%20trials%20to%20prove%20their%20products%20work%2C%20quantities%20of%20ingredients%20don't%20always%20have%20to%20be%20listed%2C%20and%20products%20are%20sometimes%20contaminated%20by%20or%20cut%20with%20other%20substances%20not%20mentioned%20on%20the%20packaging.%20One%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjamanetwork.com%2Fjournals%2Fjamanetworkopen%2Ffullarticle%2F2807343%3Futm_source%3Dtwitter%26utm_medium%3Dsocial_jamajno%26utm_term%3D10743549280%26utm_campaign%3Darticle_alert%26linkId%3D225481243%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2023%20study%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20in%20JAMA%20Network%20Open%20found%20that%2089%25%20of%20the%2057%20dietary%20supplements%20tested%20didn't%20accurately%20list%20their%20ingredients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20this%20means%20doing%20your%20homework%20before%20taking%20a%20supplement%20is%20crucial%2C%20it%20doesn't%20mean%20they%20can't%20play%20a%20role%20in%20supporting%20and%20promoting%20health%2C%20Pasiakos%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20shared%20three%20common%20misconceptions%20about%20supplements%20that%20could%20prevent%20people%20benefiting%20from%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bae5144e-ea2f-428c-9907-12d3c1c6ad15%5C%22%3E1)%20The%20more%20supplements%2C%20the%20better%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20vitamins%2C%20minerals%2C%20and%20nutrients%2C%20more%20is%20not%20always%20better%2C%20Pasiakos%20said.%20It's%20common%20for%20people%20to%20think%20that%20because%20something%20is%20%26quot%3Bnatural%26quot%3B%20you%20can't%20have%20too%20much%20of%20it%2C%20but%20that's%20untrue%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20instances%20where%20consuming%20above%20and%20beyond%20what's%20recommended%20is%20unsafe%2C%20and%20for%20a%20lot%20of%20natural%20products%2C%20we%20simply%20don't%20know%20where%20those%20upper%20levels%20are%2C%20Pasiakos%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20people%20take%20above%20the%20recommended%20daily%20limit%20of%20a%20supplement%2C%20the%20effects%20can%20be%20serious.%20In%20May%202023%2C%20a%20man%20died%20after%20taking%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fman-killed-by-vitamin-d-supplements-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etoo%20much%20vitamin%20D%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20nine%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frisks-popular-supplements-vitamin-d-magnesium-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOverdosing%20on%20magnesium%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20can%20in%20extreme%20cases%2C%20cause%20paralysis%20and%20death%2C%20while%20overdosing%20on%20vitamin%20C%20can%20lead%20to%20kidney%20problems%20and%20vitamin%20B12%20deficiencies%2C%20professor%20Rob%20Chilcott%2C%20the%20head%20of%20toxicology%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Hertfordshire%2C%20UK%2C%20previously%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222121%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20browses%20the%20supplement%20aisle%20in%20a%20store.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66fff609a7031864927f751d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMore%20than%20half%20of%20Americans%20took%20some%20kind%20of%20supplement%20in%202021%2C%20according%20to%20the%20CDC.%20%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2214b98670-a04a-4851-b255-b229a967fb8a%5C%22%3E2)%20Supplements%20are%20'tainted%20and%20adulterated'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20tend%20to%20fall%20into%20two%20camps%2C%20those%20who%20think%20all%20supplements%20are%20%26quot%3Btainted%20and%20adulterated%26quot%3B%20and%20others%20who%20think%20they%20all%20work%2C%20Pasiakos%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPasiakos%20said%20that%20certain%20resources%2C%20such%20as%20the%20ODS's%20supplement%20fact%20sheets%2C%20can%20help%20people%20make%20informed%20decisions%20about%20supplements%2C%20while%20the%20third%20party%20NSF%20Product%20Certification%20program%20can%20guarantee%20a%20product%20contains%20what%20the%20label%20says%20it%20does.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it's%20important%20to%20know%20that%20verification%20programs%20are%20not%20backing%20any%20health%20claims%20a%20company%20might%20make%20about%20their%20product.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20simply%20saying%20that%20what's%20on%20the%20label%20is%20in%20the%20dietary%20supplement%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20I%20would%20say%20is%20that%20people%20make%20sure%20that%20they%20become%20educated%20on%20these%20products%2C%20understand%20what's%20in%20them%2C%20and%20know%20that%20the%20industry%20is%20not%20out%20to%20get%20them.%20But%20there%20are%20certainly%20aspects%20of%20certain%20dietary%20supplements%20that%20may%20be%20considered%20unsafe%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229b3c3c37-ffd3-424f-984c-6059a8335205%5C%22%3E3)%20Supplements%20are%20a%20silver%20bullet%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPasiakos%20said%20people%20are%20always%20looking%20for%20a%20silver%20bullet%20to%20make%20them%20healthy%2C%20but%20they%20won't%20find%20it%20in%20dietary%20supplements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20many%20dietitians%2C%20Pasiakos%20takes%20a%20food-first%20approach%20to%20his%20health.%20He%20sees%20supplements%20as%20complementary%20to%20a%20healthy%20diet%2C%20not%20as%20a%20way%20to%20replace%20or%20substitute%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20look%20at%20dietary%20supplements%20without%20understanding%20the%20underlying%20diet%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20If%20you%20don't%20know%20what%20a%20person%20is%20eating%20and%20getting%20from%20their%20diet%20nutrient-wise%2C%20you%20can't%20advise%20them%20on%20what%20dietary%20supplements%20they%20should%20take%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can't%20just%20ignore%20that.%20So%20that's%20why%20I%20look%20at%20it%20that%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsupplements-myths-us-top-supplement-expert-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3