l%20fate%20of%20Chief%20Minister%20Nayab%20Singh%20Saini%2C%20Bhupinder%20Singh%20Hooda%2C%20and%201%2C000%20other%20candidates%20contesting%20in%20the%20state%20assembly%20elections.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fharyana-elections-2024-voting-live-updates-haryana-polls-2024-haryana-voting-elections-in-haryana-6720940%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2225-Km%20Trek%2C%20Pincer%20Movement%3A%20How%20Security%20Forces%20Gunned%20Down%2031%20Maoists%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20dense%2C%20uncharted%20forests%20of%20Abujhmad%20-%20often%20referred%20to%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bhills%20of%20the%20unknown%26quot%3B%20%C2%A0-%20in%20Bastar%20have%20long%20been%20a%20Maoist%20stronghold%2C%20shrouded%20in%20mystery%20and%20largely%20inaccessible%20to%20security%20forces.%20On%20Friday%2C%20this%20remote%20region%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20became%20the%20backdrop%20for%20one%20of%20the%20most%20significant%20encounters%20in%20recent%20history%20which%20has%20dealt%20a%20big%20blow%20to%20left-wing%20extremism%20in%20the%20region.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20massive%20operation%2C%20security%20forces%20killed%2031%20Maoists%2C%20including%20Kamlesh%20alias%20RK%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most-wanted%20Maoist%20commanders%2C%20and%20Niti%20alias%20Urmila%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20group.%20Both%20were%20key%20figures%20in%20the%20Dandakaranya%20Special%20Zonal%20Committee%20(DKSZC)%2C%20with%20Kamlesh%20being%20wanted%20in%20five%20states%20and%20Urmila%20playing%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20the%20Maoist%20propaganda%20machinery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fituhnhj8_maoists-killed_625x300_05_October_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKamlesh%2C%20originally%20from%20Vijayawada%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20was%20a%20student%20of%20the%20Civil%20Industrial%20Training%20Institute%20(ITI).%20He%20was%20primarily%20active%20in%20North%20Bastar%2C%20Nalgonda%20in%20Telangana%2C%20Manpur%20in%20Bihar%20and%20the%20Odisha%20border%20regions%2C%20and%20his%20influence%20extended%20across%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20Telangana%2C%20Odisha%20and%20Maharashtra.%20Urmila%2C%20a%20native%20of%20Gangalur%20in%20Bijapur%2C%20was%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Special%20Zonal%20Committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGunfight%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20operation%20was%20planned%20after%20intelligence%20reports%20suggested%20the%20presence%20of%20at%20least%2050%20Maoists%2C%20including%20key%20figures%20from%20the%20Indravati%20Area%20Committee%20and%20the%20People's%20Liberation%20Guerrilla%20Army%20Company%20No.%206%20in%20the%20region.%20Specific%20intelligence%20pointed%20to%20Kamlesh%2C%20Urmila%2C%20another%20wanted%20commander%20called%20Nandu%20and%20other%20Maoists%20hiding%20in%20the%20dense%20forest%20areas%20between%20the%20Thulthuli%20and%20Nendur%20villages%20in%20the%20Orchha%20and%20Barsur%20police%20station%20limits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20joint%20operation%20was%20launched%20by%20the%20District%20Reserve%20Guard%20(DRG)%2C%20Special%20Task%20Force%20(STF)%2C%20and%20additional%20reinforcements%20from%20the%20Central%20Reserve%20Police%20Force%20(CRPF).%20The%20security%20forces%2C%20after%20trekking%2025%20km%20deep%20into%20the%20forest%2C%20launched%20a%20pincer%20movement%20that%20took%20the%20Maoists%20by%20surprise.%20The%20gunfight%20continued%20for%20hours%2C%20covering%20an%20additional%2010%20km.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F0ivjma6g_maoist-encounter_625x300_05_October_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20said%20the%20encounter%20has%20resulted%20in%20the%20recovery%20of%2031%20bodies%20so%20far.%20%26quot%3BWeapons%20like%20light%20machine%20guns%20(LMGs)%2C%20AK-47s%2C%20self-loading%20rifles%20(SLRs)%2C%20INSAS%20rifles%2C%20and%20.303%20calibre%20firearms%20were%20seized%20from%20the%20site%2C%20further%20indicating%20the%20presence%20of%20senior%20Maoist%20cadres%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20official%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20DRG%20jawan%2C%20Ramchandra%20Yadav%2C%20was%20injured%20in%20the%20crossfire%20but%20has%20been%20safely%20evacuated%20and%20is%20reported%20to%20be%20stable.%20A%20search%20operation%20is%20on%20and%20forces%20are%20also%20combing%20the%20surrounding%20areas%20to%20capture%20any%20surviving%20Maoists%20who%20may%20have%20fled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3%20Successes%20In%206%20Months%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20encounter%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20major%20success%20in%20the%20ongoing%20efforts%20to%20dismantle%20Left-wing%20extremism%20in%20the%20Bastar%20region%20and%20is%20the%20biggest%20setback%20for%20Maoists%20since%20the%20Kanker%20operation%20in%20April.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20April%2015%2C%20a%20massive%20encounter%20had%20led%20to%20the%20death%20of%2029%20Maoists%2C%20including%2015%20women%2C%20in%20Kanker%20district.%20Among%20the%20dead%20were%20two%20DVCM%20(Divisional%20Committee)-level%20leaders%2C%20each%20carrying%20a%20bounty%20of%20Rs%208%20lakh.%20The%20firefight%20lasted%20for%20over%20five%20and%20a%20half%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFour%20months%20later%2C%20on%20August%2029%2C%20a%20major%20encounter%20took%20place%20on%20the%20Narayanpur%20and%20Kanker%20border%20in%20the%20Abujhmad%20region%20of%20Chhattisgarh.%20Three%20uniformed%20woman%20Maoists%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20operation%20and%20were%20identified%20as%20members%20of%20the%20North%20Bastar%20Division%20Committee%20and%20the%20People's%