%20that%20this%20will%20bring%20smiles%20to%20their%20faces.%20I%20personally%20consider%20this%20as%20a%20very%20positive%20move%20to%20reform%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20decision%20was%20reached%20that%20the%20inmates%2C%20who%20work%20as%20cooks%2C%20would%20prepare%20the%20delicacies%20during%20the%20Durga%20puja%20festivities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20delicacies%20to%20tickle%20the%20taste%20buds%20of%20the%20inmates%20will%20consist%20of%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20items%20-%20'Macher%20matha%20diye%20pui%20shak'%20(Malabar%20spinach%20with%20fish%20head)%2C%20'macher%20matha%20diye%20dal'%20(dal%20with%20fish%20head)%2C%20'luchi-cholar%20dal'%20(puri%20and%20Bengali%20chana%20dal)%2C%20'payesh'%20(Bengali%20porridge)%2C%20chicken%20curry%2C%20'alu%20potol%20chingri'%20(shrimp%20with%20pointed%20gourd%20and%20potato)%2C%20mutton%20biryani%20with%20'raita'%20(mixed%20curd)%20and%20'basanti%20pulao'%20(yellow%20pulao)%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20to%20respect%20the%20religious%20sentiment%20of%20the%20inmates%2C%20non-vegetarian%20food%20will%20not%20be%20served%20to%20everyone%20and%20the%20prisoners%20will%20be%20asked%20to%20choose%20items%2C%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20bring%20changes%20in%20their%20routine%2C%20a%20break%20from%20their%20daily%20lives.%20For%20many%20Bengalis%20or%20even%20people%20of%20different%20communities%20living%20in%20the%20state%20for%20years%2C%20Durga%20puja%20and%20other%20festivals%20are%20incomplete%20without%20fish%20and%20meat%20items%20on%20their%20platter.%20Hence%20we%20tried%20to%20bring%20variety%20in%20their%20cuisines%20so%20that%20they%20will%20relish%20as%20Bengalis%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20city%20correctional%20homes%2C%20Presidency%20Jail%2C%20currently%20houses%20former%20state%20ministers%20Partha%20Chatterjee%20and%20Jyoti%20Priya%20Mallick%20and%20R%20G%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital's%20ex-principal%20Sandip%20Ghosh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChatterjee%20is%20accused%20of%20being%20involved%20in%20school%20recruitment%20scams%20and%20Mallick%20in%20irregularities%20in%20the%20public%20distribution%20system%20while%20Ghosh%20has%20been%20charged%20with%20tampering%20with%20evidence%20in%20the%20rape-murder%20of%20a%20woman%20doctor%20and%20a%20financial%20scam%20in%20the%20R%20G%20Kar%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAltogether%2026%2C994%20men%20and%201%2C778%20women%20are%20now%20lodged%20in%2059%20correctional%20homes%20in%20the%20state%2C%20another%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20every%20major%20event%2C%20we%20seek%20to%20make%20special%20arrangements%20for%20the%20inmates%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20change%20in%20the%20menu%20during%20the%20festive%20season%20will%20be%20effected%20across%20all%20the%20correctional%20homes%2C%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728112500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fk8u4joo8_mutton-biryani_625x300_05_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmutton-biryani-chicken-curry-to-be-served-to-west-bengal-prisoners-during-durga-puja-6721113%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20changed%20menu%20for%20inmates%20-%20both%20convicts%20and%20undertrials%20-%20for%20lunch%20and%20dinner%20would%20be%20effective%20from%20Sasthi%20(October%209)%20to%20Dashami%20(October%2012)%2C%20covering%20the%20beginning%20and%20end%20of%20Durga%20puja%2C%20he%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmutton-biryani-chicken-curry-to-be-served-to-west-bengal-prisoners-during-durga-puja-6721113%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22