EPolice%20said%20that%20the%20girl%2C%20a%20minor%2C%20had%20left%20to%20attend%20a%20coaching%20class%20in%20South%2024%20Parganas'%20in%20Mahishamari%20on%20Friday%20and%20the%20family%20filed%20a%20missing%20complaint%20at%20night%20after%20she%20did%20not%20return%20home.%20Her%20body%20was%20found%20in%20a%20field%20around%203.30%20am%20on%20Saturday%20with%20multiple%20injuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20body%20was%20recovered%2C%20angry%20residents%20of%20the%20area%20started%20a%20protest%20and%20also%20set%20a%20police%20camp%20on%20fire%20after%20vandalising%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20father%20of%20the%20girl%20said%20that%20she%20had%20informed%20him%20that%20she%20would%20head%20home%20after%20the%20class%20and%20when%20he%20saw%20that%20she%20wasn't%20back%20even%20after%20he%20reached%20the%20house%2C%20the%20family%20approached%20the%20police%20outpost%20nearby%20and%20were%20directed%20to%20the%20nearest%20police%20station.%20The%20police%20said%20an%20investigation%20was%20launched%20as%20soon%20as%20the%20complaint%20was%20received.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20said%20a%2019-year-old%20man%2C%20Mostakin%20Sardar%2C%20has%20been%20arrested%20for%20the%20kidnapping%20and%20murder.%20Protesters%20carrying%20sticks%20and%20brooms%20are%20still%20out%20in%20the%20streets%2C%20however%2C%20and%20a%20large%20police%20team%20has%20been%20deployed%20to%20ensure%20the%20situation%20does%20not%20escalate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20Minister%20and%20BJP%20State%20President%20Sukanta%20Majumdar%20claimed%20that%20the%20girl%20was%20raped%2C%20and%20called%20for%20Chief%20Minister%20Banerjee's%20resignation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDurga%20Puja%20celebrations%20are%20days%20away%20and%20such%20crimes%20are%20taking%20place%20in%20the%20state%20with%20innocent%20girls%20as%20the%20victims.%20This%20shows%20that%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20has%20no%20control%20over%20the%20administration%2C%20which%20has%20become%20completely%20political.%20The%20