%3EOctober%205%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fharyana-voting-2024-haryana-votes-today-bjp-eyes-hat-trick-congress-a-comeback-10-points-6718303%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll%5C%22%3EHaryana's%20chief%20ministerial%20face%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Mr%20Jindal%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHe%20(Anil%20Vij)%20is%20also%20a%20very%20big%20leader%20of%20our%20party%20and%20time%20will%20tell%20who%20becomes%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20but%20if%20a%20big%20leader%20has%20something%20in%20mind%2C%20he%20has%20the%20right%20to%20say%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVoting%20began%20for%2090%20assembly%20seats%20in%20Haryana%20on%20Saturday%20and%20saw%20a%20voter%20turnout%20of%209.53%20per%20cent%20till%209%20AM%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20data%20shared%20by%20the%20ECI%2C%20Jind%20recorded%20the%20highest%20poll%20percentage%20of%2012.71%20per%20cent%2C%20followed%20by%20Palwal%2012.45%20per%20cent%2C%20Ambala%2011.%2087%20per%20cent%2C%20Fatehabad%2011.81%20per%20cent%2C%20and%20Mahendragarh%2011.51%20per%20cent%20till%209%20AM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFaridabad%20recorded%20an%208.82%20per%20cent%20turnout%2C%20whereas%20Gurgaon%20had%206.10%20per%20cent%2C%20Hisar%208.49%20per%20cent%20and%20Jhajjar%208.43%20per%20cent%20turnout%20till%209%20AM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20shortly%20after%20casting%20his%20vote%2C%20Union%20Minister%20and%20former%20Haryana%20chief%20minister%20Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar%20launched%20an%20all-out%20attack%20on%20the%20Congress%2C%20accusing%20it%20of%20spreading%20lies%20and%20arguing%20that%20their%20past%20corruption%20led%20to%20unemployment.%3Cbr%3E%5CnHe%20claimed%20that%20under%20BJP%20rule%2C%20employment%20opportunities%20have%20increased%2C%20particularly%20in%20Haryana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Khattar%20served%20as%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Haryana%20for%20around%209.5%20years.%20He%20was%20succeeded%20by%20Nayab%20Singh%20Saini%20in%20March%20this%20year.%20BJP%20is%20contesting%20the%20polls%20under%20his%20leadership.%20Saini%20is%20contesting%20from%20the%20Ladwa%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20election%20is%20a%20high-stakes%20battle%20as%20the%20BJP%20is%20eyeing%20a%20third%20straight%20term%20to%20power%20in%20the%20state%2C%20the%20Congress%20party%20is%20aiming%20to%20wrest%20back%20power%20riding%20on%20anti-incumbency%2C%20and%20issues%20of%20farmer%20protests%20and%20wrestler%20protests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20key%20contesting%20parties%20in%20Haryana%20include%20the%20BJP%2C%20Congress%2C%20and%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20pre-poll%20alliance%20between%20the%20Indian%20National%20Lok%20Dal-Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20(INLD-BSP)%20and%20the%20Jannayak%20Janta%20Party%20(JJP)-Azad%20Samaj%20Party%20(ASP).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20total%20of%201%2C031%20candidates%20are%20contesting%20in%20all%2090%20assembly%20constituencies%2C%20and%2020%2C632%20polling%20booths%20have%20been%20set%20up%20for%20voting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20results%20for%20the%20Haryana%20Assembly%20elections%20will%20be%20declared%20along%20with%20those%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20on%20October%208.In%20the%202019%20Assembly%20elections%2C%20the%20BJP%20won%2040%20of%20the%2090%20seats%2C%20forming%20a%20coalition%20government%20with%20the%20JJP%2C%20which%20won%2010%20seats.%20The%20Congress%20secured%2031%20seats.%20However%2C%20JJP%20later%20broke%20out%20of%20the%20coalition.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728108960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F578qkdeg_naveen-jindal_625x300_05_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fharyana-assembly-elections-2024-naveen-jindal-its-considered-auspicious-bjp-mp-goes-to-poll-on-a-horse-6720779%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22BJP%20MP%20Naveen%20Jindal%20today%20cast%20his%20vote%20for%20the%20H