d-moments-before-fatally-shooting-him-in-courthouse%2Famp_articleshow%2F113957195.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Did%20Harmanpreet%20Cross%20The%20Line%20Or%20Umpire%20Committed%20Mistake%3A%20Rules%20Say...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20India%20vs%20New%20Zealand%20Women's%20T20%20World%20Cup%20saw%20a%20big%20controversy%20erupt%20over%20a%20run-out%20call%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Harmanpreet%20Kaur%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F59824-harmanpreet-kaur-bhullar-playerprofile%5C%22%3EHarmanpreet%20Kaur%3C%2Fa%3E-led%20team.%20In%20the%2014th%20over%2C%20the%20Indian%20players%20appealed%20for%20a%20run%20out%20against%20New%20Zealand's%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Amelia%20Kerr%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F117762-amelia-kerr-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAmelia%20Kerr%3C%2Fa%3E.%20After%20a%20miscommunication%20during%20a%20run-out%20attempt%2C%20the%20ball%20was%20declared%20dead%2C%20sparking%20heated%20discussions%20between%20Indian%20captain%20Harmanpreet%20Kaur%20and%20the%20umpires.%20Despite%20this%2C%20Kerr%20was%20dismissed%20two%20balls%20later.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Laws%20of%20Cricket%2C%20the%20incident%20was%20quite%20ambiguous%20and%20a%20mistake%20of%20sorts%20was%20committed%20by%20either%20side.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaw%2020%2C%20clause%2020.1%20states%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20ball%20shall%20be%20considered%20to%20be%20dead%20when%20it%20is%20clear%20to%20the%20bowler's%20end%20umpire%20that%20the%20fielding%20side%20and%20both%20batters%20at%20the%20wicket%20have%20ceased%20to%20regard%20it%20as%20in%20play.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Kerr%20attempeted%20a%20second%20run%20and%20India%20went%20for%20a%20run%20out%2C%20it%20may%20mean%20neither%20stopped%20to%20regard%20it%20in%20play.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Clause%2020.6%20states%3A%20%26quot%3BOnce%20the%20ball%20is%20dead%2C%20no%20revoking%20of%20any%20decision%20can%20bring%20the%20ball%20back%20into%20play%20for%20that%20delivery.%26quot%3B%20That%20umpires%20had%20declared%20the%20ball%20dead%2C%20hence%20there%20is%20no%20coming%20back%20from%20there.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0In%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20Women's%20T20%20World%20Cup%2C%20many%20people%20including%20the%20Indian%20players%2C%20talked%20about%20how%20this%20was%20the%20best-ever%20team%20to%20play%20in%20an%20edition%20of%20the%20tournament%2C%20with%20all%20bases%20covered.%20But%20Harmanpreet%20Kaur%20%26amp%3B%20co%2C%20the%20pre-tournament%20favourites%2C%20were%20off%20to%20a%20rough%20start%20in%20Group%20A%20with%20insipid%20performances%20across%20all%20facets%20and%20slumped%20to%20a%20heavy%2058-run%20defeat%20to%20New%20Zealand%20at%20the%20Dubai%20International%20Stadium%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20didn't%20play%20our%20best%20cricket.%20Going%20forward%20we%20know%20every%20game%20is%20important.%20We%20created%20chances%20but%20we%20were%20not%20able%20to%20avail%20those%20chances.%20They%20played%20better%20cricket%20than%20us%2C%20no%20doubt%20about%20that.%20(In)%20Fielding%20we%20made%20some%20mistakes%20so%20that%20is%20a%20learning%20for%20us%20going%20forward.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20chased%20160-170%20many%20times%2C%20we%20were%20expecting%20that%20on%20the%20board.%20While%20batting%2C%20we%20knew%20someone%20had%20to%20bat%20through%20but%20we%20kept%20losing%20wickets.%20We%20know%20this%20group%20is%20capable%20of%20(doing)%20better%2C%20this%20wasn't%20the%20start%20we%20were%20expecting%20but%20we%20have%20to%20go%20(up)%20from%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20disappointed%20Harmanpreet%20after%20the%20match%20ended.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728106620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Ffaadbf58_harmanpreet-kaur-umpire_625x300_05_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwomen-s-t20-world-cup%2Fdid-h