uitable%20marriage%20proposal%20for%20you%3F%E2%80%99%20I%20also%20remember%20people%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%98What%20will%20you%20do%20with%20so%20much%20education%E2%80%99.%20%5BAfter%20listening%20to%20such%20comments%5D%20I%20decided%20to%20be%20independent%20and%20do%20something%20on%20my%20own%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Pooja%2C%20a%20native%20of%20Pune%2C%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20a%20master%E2%80%99s%20degree%20in%20computer%20science%2C%20she%20joined%20a%20reputed%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F307590%2Festher-foundation-fellowship-programme-helping-bahujan-women-find-jobs-in-accenture-tcs-genpact%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emultinational%20company%20%3C%2Fa%3E(MNC).%20What%20she%20witnessed%20there%20would%20go%20on%20to%20determine%20her%20professional%20choices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20very%20junior%20employee%20of%20an%20MNC%2C%20I%20remember%20the%20struggle%20my%20female%20manager%20went%20through%20for%20her%20promotions%20and%20on-site%20opportunities.%20Working%20at%20that%20company%20for%20two%20or%20three%20years%2C%20I%20always%20saw%20her%20professional%20ambitions%20stifled%20compared%20to%20other%20male%20managers%20in%20the%20company%20despite%20her%20experience%20and%20skills%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CShe%20never%20got%20on-site%20opportunities%20that%20other%20male%20managers%20had%20because%20she%20was%20judged%20for%20having%20two%20children.%20Nobody%20asked%20her%20whether%20her%20family%20was%20flexible%20to%20the%20idea%20of%20working%20on-site.%20She%20would%20work%20round%20the%20clock%2C%20support%20every%20member%20of%20her%20team%2C%20and%20even%20support%20her%20colleagues%20working%20on-site%20even%20though%20that%20opportunity%20was%20denied%20to%20her.%20I%20vividly%20remember%20feeling%20very%20bad%20for%20her.%20I%20desperately%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20for%20her%20but%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20because%20I%20was%20still%20a%20very%20junior%20employee%20with%20no%20voice%20or%20power%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20college%2C%20however%2C%20she%20kept%20in%20touch%20with%20her%20friend%20and%20batchmate%20Tejas%20Kulkarni%2C%20who%20is%20now%20the%20CEO%20of%20%3Cem%3ESheWork.in%3C%2Fem%3E.%20As%20Pooja%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CDuring%20our%20many%20discussions%2C%20Tejas%20and%20I%20always%20envisioned%20wanting%20to%20do%20something%20for%20women%20working%20in%20the%20tech%20industry.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20Pooja%20and%20Tejas%20quit%20their%20respective%20jobs%20at%20different%20MNCs%20and%20started%20their%20software%20company%20called%20Telemerge%20IT%20Services%20Pvt%20Ltd%20alongside%20Pune-based%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F356672%2Fenmasse-epic-stories-video-contest-entrepreneurial-households-startups-businesses-investors-small-town-rural-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eentrepreneur%20%3C%2Fa%3ETushar%20Kulkarni%20and%20made%20their%20foray%20into%20the%20tech%20industry.%20At%20the%20outset%2C%20they%20established%20an%20informal%20rule%20that%20they%20would%20give%20more%20opportunities%20to%20women%20in%20their%20company%20to%20identify%20how%20it%20goes%2C%20before%20solving%20this%20problem%20for%20bigger%20tech%20companies%20in%20India.%20Suffice%20it%20to%20say%20that%20they%20encountered%20different%20challenges%20when%20it%20came%20to%20hiring%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20running%20Telemerge%2C%20they%20learnt%20that%20women%20looking%20to%20rejoin%20the%20workforce%20after%20a%20sabbatical%20or%20maternity%20leave%20were%20hesitant%20to%20get%20a%20job%20in%20the%20tech%20industry%20because%20they%20felt%20trapped%2C%20found%20travelling%20a%20challenge%2C%20and%20were%20struggling%20to%20strike%20a%20balance%20between%20household%20and%20office%20work.%20This%20was%20a%20problem%20they%20were%20going%20to%20target.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSheWork.in-co-founders-1728051534.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22SheWork%20is%20helping%20women%20in%20technology%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSheWork.in-co-founders-1728051534.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSheWork.in-co-founders-1728051534-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSheWork.in-co-founders-1728051534-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSheWork.in-co-founders-1728051534-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSheWork.in-co-founders-1728051534-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-368852%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPooja%20Bangad%20and%20Tejas%20Kulkarni%2C%20co-founders%20of%20SheWork.in%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20tried%20to%20identify%20other%20such%20problems.%20By%20March%202020%20we%20created%20our%20own%20platform%20called%20%3Cem%3ESheWork.in%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20specifically%20for%20women%20talent%20in%20India%2C%20under%20the%20aegis%20of%20Telemerge.%20As%20a%20priority%2C%20we%20have%20created%20a%20community%20where%20our%20talent%20advocates%2Fmentors%20talk%20to%20women%20(particularly%20those%20coming%20back%20to%20work%20after%20a%20sabbatical)%20and%20help%20them%20restart%20their%20careers%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Pooja.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20joined%20hands%20together%20to%20launch%20%3Cem%3ESheWork.in%3C%2Fem%3E%20because%20Tejas%20was%20inclined%20to%20my%20aims%20and%20supported%20my%20vision%20to%20start%20this%20initiative%20exclusively%20for%20women.%20Given%20my%20experience%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20help%20more%20women%20to%20become%20financially%20independent%20so%20that%20they%20have%20the%20freedom%20to%20choose%20their%20path%20and%20not%20be%20stifled%20by%20their%20parents%2C%20husbands%2C%20or%20families%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20time%2C%20they%20collaborated%20with%20companies%20like%20Xebia%2C%20Tata%20Consultancy%20Services%2C%20Tech%20Mahindra%2C%20etc.%20Today%2C%20%3Cem%3ESheWork.in%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20partnering%20with%20more%20than%20150%20companies%20of%20different%20scales.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20does%20SheWork.in%20solve%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20%3Cem%3ESheWork.in%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20they%20are%20solving%20the%20problem%20of%20the%20lack%20of%20women%20in%20the%20tech%20industry%2C%20primarily%20in%20leadership%20or%20mid-level%20roles%20working%20on%20specified%20technologies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F323501%2Figniting-ideas-for-impact-audiobook-explores-pioneering-indian-startups%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eearlier%20conversation%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Pooja%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20trying%20to%20work%20with%20developers%20or%20people%20in%20leadership%20roles%20with%20anywhere%20between%20three%20to%2012%20years%20of%20experience.%20We%20do%20have%20plans%20in%20the%20future%20to%20help%20women%20in%20other%20industries%2C%20but%20today%2C%20our%20vision%20is%20to%20try%20and%20solve%20the%20problem%20in%20the%20tech%20industry.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20main%20focus%20is%20not%20just%20to%20solve%20the%20problem%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20talent.%20We%20also%20have%20to%20look%20at%20the%20companies%20who%20are%20going%20to%20hire%20them.%20Companies%20also%20have%20to%20trust%20women%20to%20give%20them%20a%20chance.%20Our%20focus%20lies%20in%20balancing%20their%20respective%20needs%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESheWork.in%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20focused%20on%20seamlessly%20reintegrating%20women%20with%20three%20or%20more%20years%20of%20experience%20in%20the%20tech%20industry%20back%20into%20the%20workforce%20after%20they%20had%20to%20leave%20it%20for%20reasons%20like%20marriage%2C%20relocation%2C%20childbirth%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20why%20start%20with%20women%20with%20three%20years%20of%20experience%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Pooja%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CAs%20per%20our%20statistical%20findings%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20usually%20after%20three%20years%20in%20the%20workforce%20when%20women%20get%20married%20and%20relocate%20to%20where%20their%20husbands%20work.%20Once%20they%20cross%20the%20five%20or%20six-year%20experience%20threshold%2C%20we%20find%20that%20women%20have%20their%20first%20child%2C%20go%20on%20a%20maternity%20break%2C%20and%20as%20a%20result%2C%20their%20promotions%20get%20delayed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWomen-in-Tech-3-1728052294.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Women%20in%20tech%20are%20being%20assisted%20by%20SheWork%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWomen-in-Tech-3-1728052294.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWomen-in-Tech-3-1728052294-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWomen-in-Tech-3-1728052294-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWomen-in-Tech-3-1728052294-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWomen-in-Tech-3-1728052294-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-368860%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERepresentational%20Image%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20percentage%20of%20women%20in%20leadership%20positions%20in%20the%20tech%20industry%20is%20still%20very%20low%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Pooja%20Bangad%2C%20co-founder%20of%20SheWork.in%20(Image%20courtesy%20Shutterstock%2Finsta_photos)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20goes%20on%20to%20elaborate%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20percentage%20of%20women%20in%20leadership%20positions%20in%20the%20tech%20industry%20is%20still%20very%20low.%20Our%20focus%20is%20to%20first%20increase%20diversity%20at%20the%20leadership%20or%20C-level%20(chief-level%20jobs%20that%20are%20the%20highest%20tier%20of%20executive%20jobs%20within%20an%20organisation).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20management%20is%20liberal%20or%20open%20to%20hiring%20more%20women%20at%20their%20level%2C%20that%20is%20when%20they%20will%20guide%20their%20subordinate%20teams%20to%20hire%20more%20women.%20See%2C%20the%20market%20is%20very%20competitive.%20Nobody%20wants%20the%20other%20person%20to%20get%20ahead%20of%20them.%20This%20is%20why%20our%20journey%20to%20make%20the%20workplace%20in%20the%20tech%20industry%20more%20inclusive%20starts%20at%20the%20leadership%20level%20because%20that%E2%80%99s%20where%20they%20are%20going%20to%20promote%20and%20help%20women%20come%20back%20and%20rejoin%20the%20workforce%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESheWork.in%3C%2Fem%3E%20helps%20companies%20to%20hire%20more%20women.%20But%20this%20does%20not%20mean%20they%20ask%20companies%20to%20give%20their%20women%20applicants%20only%20remote%20working%20opportunities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20not%20asking%20them%20to%20establish%20exclusive%20policies%20to%20hire%20women%20but%20inclusive%20ones.%20Speaking%20to%20companies%2C%20we%20explain%20to%20them%20why%20it%20is%20important%20that%20they%20also%20give%20women%20an%20opportunity%20for%20the%20same%20role%20as%20they%20give%20men.%20Unlike%20days%20in%20the%20past%2C%20women%20today%20also%20travel%20and%20do%20night%20or%20second%20shifts%20while%20technology%20has%20upgraded%20and%20companies%20have%20the%20salary%20cap%20space.%20So%2C%20why%20not%20hire%20more%20capable%20women%20instead%20of%20leaving%20them%20out%3F%E2%80%9D%20says%20Pooja.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20particularly%20unique%20about%20%3Cem%3ESheWork.in%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20that%20they%20are%20focused%20on%20delivering%20well-experienced%20talent%20for%20tech%20companies%20with%20a%20turnaround%20time%20of%2024%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWomen-in-Tech-1-1728052022.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22This%20venture%20is%20looking%20to%20diversify%20the%20workplace%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWomen-in-Tech-1-1728052022.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWomen-in-Tech-1-1728052022-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWomen-in-Tech-1-1728052022-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWomen-in-Tech-1-1728052022-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWomen-in-Tech-1-1728052022-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-368856%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERepresentational%20Image%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20women%20to%20have%20more%20opportunities%20in%20tech%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Pooja%20(Image%20courtesy%20yurakrasil%2Fshutterstock)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20get%20a%20requirement%20from%20a%20company%2C%20we%20give%20them%20matching%20job%20profiles%20within%2024%20hours.%20Following%20this%2C%20you%20have%20the%20standard%20hiring%20process%20by%20a%20company.%20Once%20the%20company%20completes%20their%20rounds%20of%20tests%20and%20interviews%2C%20the%20person%20who%20is%20selected%20joins%20the%20company%20within%20a%20day.%20We%20are%20focussed%20on%20delivering%20the%20right%20job%20(for%20the%20candidate)%2C%20and%20the%20right%20candidate%20(for%20the%20company)%20at%20the%20right%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20claims%20Pooja.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20terms%20of%20job%20profiles%2C%20we%20are%20focused%20on%20project%20managers%2C%20designers%2C%20mobile-based%20application%20developers%2C%20web-based%20application%20developers%2C%20the%20front%20end%2C%20back%20end%2C%20full%20stack%20developers%2C%20testers%2C%20etc.%20We%20want%20women%20to%20have%20more%20opportunities%20in%20tech%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20is%20the%20current%20state%20of%20women%20in%20the%20tech%20industry%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESheWork.in%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20currently%20working%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20companies%20that%20are%20hiring%20talent%20through%20the%20robust%20online%20community%20they%20have%20developed.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EShework.in%3C%2Fem%3E%20offers%20a%20platform%20called%20%3Cem%3ETech%20Pundit%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20connects%20mentors%20and%20mentees%20for%20personalised%20guidance%20and%20learning%20experiences.%20When%20we%20have%20tech%20mentors%20talking%20to%20women%20in%20our%20%3Cem%3ESheWork.in%3C%2Fem%3E%20community%2C%20we%20help%20them%20navigate%20the%20latest%20trends%20in%20technology%20and%20what%20skills%20they%20currently%20lack.%20Through%20our%20community%2C%20we%20are%20trying%20to%20help%20them%20up-skill%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Pooja.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20despite%20regularly%20hearing%20catchphrases%20like%20%E2%80%98diversity%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98diversity%20hiring%E2%80%99%20during%20recruitment%20drives%20by%20various%20companies%2C%20Pooja%20observes%20that%20they%20are%20not%20ready%20to%20give%20women%20equal%20pay%20despite%20having%20the%20requisite%20skill%20set.%20That%20is%20a%20major%20challenge%20they%20face.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20still%20have%20to%20convince%20companies%20to%20upgrade%20their%20salary%20packages%20for%20women.%20If%20companies%20offer%20a%20person%20a%20certain%20job%20profile%20because%20they%20are%20capable%2C%20they%20should%20also%20pay%20them%20accordingly.%20That%20is%20something%20which%20I%20feel%20is%20still%20lacking%20in%20the%20tech%20industry%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20they%20hire%2C%20for%20example%2C%20a%20person%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98Project%20Lead%E2%80%99%2C%20they%20are%20doing%20so%20because%20they%20find%20their%20skill%20sets%20appropriate.%20As%20a%20company%2C%20they%20are%20not%20hiring%20talent%20because%20they%20want%20to%20fill%20up%20some%20diversity%20ratio.%20After%20all%2C%20that%20will%20affect%20productivity%20and%20profits%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWomen-in-Tech-4-1728052526.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22This%20startup%20is%20a%20pioneer%20in%20India%20promoting%20women%20in%20tech%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWomen-in-Tech-4-1728052526.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWomen-in-Tech-4-1728052526-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWomen-in-Tech-4-1728052526-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWomen-in-Tech-4-1728052526-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWomen-in-Tech-4-1728052526-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-368864%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERepresentational%20Imge%3A%20%E2%80%9CStatistics%20largely%20show%20that%20women%20earn%2020%20to%2030%20percent%20less%20than%20men%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Pooja%20(Image%20courtesy%20Shutterstock%2FGorodenkoff)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Pooja%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F295810%2Fgender-equality-at-workplace-accenture-empowers-women-for-leadership%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egender%20pay%20gap%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20tech%20industry%20stands%20at%20about%2020%20to%2030%20percent.%20This%20isn%E2%80%99t%20a%20definitive%20figure%20and%20it%20depends%20on%20things%20like%20the%20number%20of%20gap%20years%20a%20person%20has%20taken%20from%20the%20workforce%20%E2%80%9Cbut%20statistics%20largely%20show%20that%20women%20earn%2020%20to%2030%20percent%20less%20than%20men%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20a%20woman%20has%20not%20worked%20for%20three%20years%2C%20but%20has%20taken%20the%20necessary%20training%20and%20courses%20to%20make%20up%20for%20that%20gap%2C%20they%20are%20offered%20a%20salary%20of%20juniors%20with%20two%20to%20three%20years%20of%20experience.%20Recently%2C%20I%20came%20across%20a%20post%20of%20a%20company%20hiring%20project%20engineers%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F311587%2Fnashik-engineer-quit-job-to-grow-saffron-in-shipping-container-hyroponics-earn-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esoftware%20engineers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20.NET%20developers%20with%20experience%20of%20six%20to%20eight%20years.%20In%20the%20post%2C%20they%20mentioned%20a%20willingness%20to%20accept%20job%20applications%20of%20persons%20with%20a%20gap%20of%20up%20to%20four%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20feedback%20we%20got%20from%20those%20applying%20was%20that%20they%20were%20offered%20a%20salary%20of%20just%20Rs%2025%2C000%20per%20month.%20When%20asked%20why%20the%20applicants%20were%20offered%20such%20a%20low%20salary%2C%20the%20companies%20said%20that%20they%20will%20help%20applicants%20undergo%20training%20for%20three%20months.%20After%20a%20year%20of%20working%20at%20the%20company%2C%20these%20applicants%20will%20qualify%20for%20appraisals.%20Given%20the%20paucity%20of%20opportunities%2C%20many%20end%20up%20accepting%20these%20low-ball%20offers%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20unacceptable%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20is%20%3Cem%3ESheWork.in%3C%2Fem%3E%20addressing%20this%20pay%20gap%3F%20It%E2%80%99s%20difficult%20because%20they%E2%80%99re%20not%20the%20ones%20hiring.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20present%2C%20we%20are%20engaged%20with%20more%20than%20150%20companies%20to%20hire%20more%20women%20in%20their%20workforce.%20Our%20team%20speaks%20to%20these%20companies%2C%20discusses%20their%20salary%20bands%2C%20and%20tells%20them%20what%20the%20industry%20standard%20is%20and%20what%20they%20should%20ideally%20offer.%20If%20the%20companies%20express%20a%20willingness%20to%20interview%20our%20applicants%20and%20discuss%20salary%20offers%20commensurate%20with%20the%20experience%20and%20skill%20set%20of%20our%20applicants%2C%20we%20make%20the%20effort%20to%20help%20them%20diversify%20their%20workforce.%20If%20the%20companies%20are%20hesitant%2C%20we%20step%20back%20and%20ask%20our%20applicants%20not%20to%20compromise%20on%20their%20salary%20demand%20and%20not%20go%20for%20their%20interviews%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ESheWork.in%3C%2Fem%3E%20makes%20efforts%20to%20ensure%20that%20every%20person%20they%20recommend%20to%20companies%20is%20capable%20of%20taking%20these%20job%20interviews.%20In%20the%20background%2C%20we%20are%20running%20a%20lot%20of%20programmes%20to%20make%20sure%20the%20applicant%20is%20capable%20enough.%20As%20I%20said%20earlier%2C%20we%20connect%20these%20applicants%20to%20mentors%20who%20help%20them%20catch%20up%20to%20the%20latest%20trends%20in%20the%20tech%20industry%20and%20fill%20up%20the%20necessary%20gaps%20in%20their%20skill%20sets.%20Moreover%2C%20these%20mentors%20also%20interview%20our%20applicants%20for%20certain%20roles.%20So%2C%20we%20only%20deliver%20these%20interviewed%20people%20to%20the%20companies.%20So%2C%20we%20make%20sure%20that%20the%20person%20(applicant)%20is%20capable%20and%20that%20the%20%5Bjob%5D%20profiles%20are%20filtered%20at%20our%20end%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWomen-in-Tech-2-1728052657.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22SheWork%20is%20a%20Pune-based%20company%20dedicated%20to%20hiring%20women%20in%20tech%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWomen-in-Tech-2-1728052657.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWomen-in-Tech-2-1728052657-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWomen-in-Tech-2-1728052657-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWomen-in-Tech-2-1728052657-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWomen-in-Tech-2-1728052657-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-368867%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERepresentational%20Image%3A%20Companies%20need%20to%20address%20unconscious%20bias%20against%20hiring%20women%20(Image%20courtesy%20Shutterstock%2Ffizkes)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20the%20pay%20gap%2C%20Pooja%20also%20argues%20that%20at%20the%20recruiter%20level%2C%20there%20is%20still%20an%20unconscious%20bias%20against%20hiring%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20we%20see%20is%20that%20if%20companies%20receive%20five%20CVs%20(three%20women%20and%20two%20men)%2C%20they%20will%20interview%20the%20two%20men%20and%20give%20them%20priority.%20If%20these%20men%20are%20rejected%2C%20only%20then%20will%20they%20give%20the%20female%20job-seeker%20a%20chance.%20That%20unconscious%20bias%20still%20exists%20at%20the%20ground%20level.%20Despite%20all%20the%20noise%20around%20hiring%20more%20women%2C%20recruiters%20at%20the%20ground%20level%20still%20lack%20the%20confidence%20to%20do%20so.%20This%20unconscious%20bias%20has%20to%20change%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECompanies%20can%20take%20a%20variety%20of%20steps%20to%20address%20these%20biases%20by%20providing%20some%20basic%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F164442%2Fmaddie-award-mg-changemakers-gender-equity-india-news%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egender%20sensitivity%3C%2Fa%3E%20training%20to%20their%20recruiters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMeanwhile%2C%20at%20%3Cem%3ESheWork.in%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20what%20we%20do%20is%20mask%20the%20CVs%20sent%20to%20companies.%20All%20we%20give%20them%20is%20their%20first%20names%20and%20skill%20sets.%20We%20do%20not%20put%20up%20their%20marital%20status%2C%20surnames%2C%20genders%20(although%20that%E2%80%99s%20sometimes%20difficult%20with%20first%20names)%2C%20etc.%20When%20we%20send%20their%20CVs%2C%20we%20highlight%20their%20skill%20sets%2C%20the%20projects%20they%E2%80%99ve%20worked%20on%2C%20the%20work%20they%20have%20done%2C%20roles%2C%20responsibilities%2C%20etc.%20Once%20they%20are%20selected%20for%20interviews%2C%20we%20communicate%20to%20the%20panels%20at%20these%20companies%20overseeing%20hiring%20to%20record%20them.%20We%20want%20them%20to%20record%20the%20interviews%20so%20that%20our%20candidates%20aren%E2%80%99t%20asked%20questions%20that%20go%20beyond%20the%20scope%20of%20their%20professional%20capabilities.%20Recording%20these%20interviews%20makes%20recruiters%20conscious%20of%20the%20questions%20they%20ask%2C%E2%80%9D%20claims%20Pooja.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20the%20nature%20of%20work%20has%20also%20changed.%20But%20that%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20mean%20that%20%3Cem%3ESheWork.in%20%3C%2Fem%3Eapplicants%20are%20only%20looking%20for%20remote%20opportunities%20for%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20not%20telling%20companies%20to%20only%20give%20our%20applicants%20remote%20opportunities.%20The%20current%20trend%20is%20moving%20towards%20hybridisation.%20So%2C%20we%20ask%20companies%20to%20give%20our%20applicants%20hybrid%20work%20opportunities%20but%20with%20some%20flexibility%20as%20well.%20For%20example%2C%20if%20an%20applicant%20just%20had%20a%20baby%20six%20months%20ago%20and%20has%20come%20back%20from%20maternity%20leave%2C%20we%20negotiate%20with%20the%20company%20to%20go%20the%20extra%20mile.%20For%20example%2C%20if%20companies%20have%20a%20five-day%20policy%20of%20coming%20to%20the%20office%2C%20we%20help%20our%20applicant%20negotiate%20for%20three%20days%20because%20she%20has%20a%20baby%2C%E2%80%9D%20notes%20Pooja.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThankfully%2C%20we%20have%20some%20industry%20leaders%20supporting%20our%20work.%20They%20are%20lending%20us%20a%20helping%20hand%20in%20making%20their%20workplace%20more%20flexible.%20On%20our%20end%2C%20we%20encourage%20our%20applicants%20that%20if%20they%20want%20equal%20pay%20and%20opportunity%2C%20they%20also%20need%20to%20work%20a%20little%20harder%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20their%20part%2C%20%3Cem%3ESheWork.in%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20also%20come%20up%20with%20their%20%3Cem%3EGyno-Care%20Program%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20offers%20free%20health%20check%20up%20camps%20for%20women%20IT%20professionals%20in%20association%20with%20partner%20companies%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC-7w-8woDPS%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC-7w-8woDPS%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC-7w-8woDPS%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20SheWork%20(%40shework.in)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ENeed%20more%20help%20from%20families%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20her%20experience%2C%20Pooja%20believes%20that%20the%20greatest%20resistance%20%5Bto%20women%20working%20regularly%20in%20the%20tech%20industry%5D%20usually%20comes%20from%20families%20more%20than%20companies%20in%20this%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20women%20really%20need%20is%20more%20help%20from%20their%20families%20like%20their%20husbands%2C%20in-laws%2C%20and%20relatives%2C%20especially%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20household%20work.%20They%20must%20contribute%20a%20little%20more%20to%20unburden%20women%20from%20the%20responsibilities%20of%20household%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDespite%20the%20availability%20of%20daycare%20facilities%20in%20cities%2C%20there%20are%20families%20who%20do%20not%20like%20their%20children%20to%20be%20put%20up%20there.%20Of%20course%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20personal%20choice%20whether%20you%20want%20to%20put%20your%20child%20in%20a%20daycare%20facility%20or%20not%20but%20as%20times%20change%2C%20so%20should%20families.%20If%20families%20can%20support%20the%20idea%20of%20putting%20their%20children%20in%20a%20daycare%20facility%2C%20it%20would%20help%20working%20women%20a%20lot%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECompanies%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20must%20do%20more%20to%20accommodate%20women%20by%20investing%20and%20setting%20up%20creches%20and%20day-care%20facilities%20for%20children%2C%20she%20argues.%20%E2%80%9CDuring%20a%20recent%20visit%20to%20Sydney%2C%20I%20remember%20visiting%20a%20company%20that%20had%20a%20feeding%20room%20for%20new%20mothers%20and%20a%20creche%20facility%20overseen%20by%20a%20qualified%20caretaker%2C%20where%20children%20could%20play.%20Companies%20in%20India%20can%20afford%20to%20invest%20in%20such%20facilities%20and%20must%20progress%20with%20the%20times%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Images%20courtesy%20SheWork.in%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shutterstock.com%2Fimage-photo%2Fdiverse-office-portrait-talented-indian-girl-2078917600%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShutterstock%3C