e-executed-in-attacks-on-3-villages-in-burkina-faso-report-5167872%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone%20of%20the%20worst%20in%20the%20West%20African%20country's%20history%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20has%20been%20grappling%20with%20a%20jihadist%20insurgency%20waged%20by%20rebels%20affiliated%20with%20Al-Qaeda%20and%20the%20Islamic%20State%20group%20that%20spilled%20over%20from%20neighbouring%20Mali%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20members%20of%20Jama'at%20Nusrat%20al-Islam%20wal-Muslimin%20(JNIM)%2C%20an%20Al-Qaeda%20affiliate%20based%20in%20Mali%20and%20active%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbrowns-not-greens-how-an-arid-africa-country-is-reimagining-golf-courses-3876165%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBurkina%20Faso%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20shot%20down%20villagers%20as%20they%20swept%20into%20the%20outskirts%20of%20Barsalogho%20on%20bikes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20United%20Nations%20estimated%20a%20death%20count%20of%20around%20200%2C%20JNIM%20said%20it%20had%20killed%20nearly%20300%20%26quot%3Bfighters%26quot%3B.%20However%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2024%2F10%2F04%2Fafrica%2Fburkina-faso-massacre-600-dead-french-intel-intl%2Findex.html%5C%22%3ECNN%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20citing%20a%20French%20government%20security%20assessment%2C%20reported%20that%20up%20to%20600%20people%20were%20shot%20dead%20in%20the%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20man%2C%20who%20said%20he%20was%20one%20of%20dozens%20of%20men%20told%20to%20dig%20the%20trenches%20by%20the%20army%2C%20told%20CNN%20that%20he%20was%204%20kilometers%20from%20the%20town%20at%20about%2011%20am%2C%20in%20a%20trench%2C%20when%20he%20heard%20the%20first%20gunshots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20started%20to%20crawl%20into%20the%20trench%20to%20escape.%C2%A0But%20it%20seemed%20that%20the%20attackers%20were%20following%20the%20trenches.%20So%2C%20I%20crawled%20out%20and%20came%20across%20the%20first%20bloodied%20victim.%20There%20was%20blood%20everywhere%20on%20my%20way.%20There%20was%20screaming%20everywhere.%20I%20got%20down%20on%20my%20stomach%20under%20a%20bush%2C%20until%20later%20in%20the%20afternoon%2C%20hiding%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20survivor%2C%20who%20lost%20two%20members%20of%20her%20family%20in%20the%20attack%2C%20said%20JNIM%20killed%20people%20%26quot%3Ball%20day%20long%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20three%20days%20we%20were%20collecting%20bodies%20-%20scattered%20everywhere.%20Fear%20got%20into%20our%20hearts.%20At%20the%20burial%20time%2C%20there%20are%20so%20many%20bodies%20lying%20on%20the%20ground%20that%20burying%20was%20hard%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20military%20reportedly%20ordered%20the%20locals%20to%20dig%20a%20vast%20trench%20network%20around%20the%20town%20to%20protect%20it%20from%20jihadists%20circulating%20nearby.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJNIM%20has%20warned%20civilians%20against%20endorsing%20the%20army%20in%20its%20fight%20against%20the%20insurgency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20ACLED%20analysis%20group%2C%20which%20tracks%20global%20conflict%2C%20members%20affiliated%20with%20Al-Qaeda%20-%20which%20was%20founded%20by%20Osama%20bin%20Laden%20and%20carried%20out%20the%209%2F11%20attacks%20in%20the%20US%20-%20and%20the%20Islamic%20State%20group%20have%20killed%20about%203%2C800%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20start%20of%20the%20conflict%20in%202015%2C%20more%20than%2020%2C000%20people%20have%20been%20killed%20and%20over%20two%20million%20displaced%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fburkina-faso-army-announces-overthrow-of-military-government-amid-violence-3393970%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBurkina%20Faso%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20poorest%20countries%20situated%20in%20the%20Sahel%2C%20a%20region%20wracked%20by%20instability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(With%20agency%20inputs)%3C%2Fem%3E