e%20the%20same%20courage%20to%20have%20these%20conversations%20at%20home%2C%20and%20I%20know%20they%20might%20not%20always%20have%20a%20positive%20outcome.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDid%20she%20ever%20fathom%20Son%20Rise%20would%20create%20whistleblowers%20of%20patriarchy%3F%20No.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20going%20by%20her%20observations%20over%20the%20last%20three%20years%20of%20the%20film%E2%80%99s%20screening%20across%2071%20countries%20as%20part%20of%20the%20UN%E2%80%99s%20global%20%23HeForShe%20movement%2C%20the%20boy%20is%20not%20alone%20in%20wanting%20to%20fight%20gender%20bias.%20The%20sentiment%20is%20mirrored%20by%20police%20officers%2C%20CEOs%20of%20multinational%20corporations%2C%20the%20elite%2C%20as%20well%20as%20those%20in%20rural%20hinterlands%2C%20she%20has%20remarked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlways%20one%20to%20target%20the%20status%20quo%20through%20layered%20rhetorics%2C%20Bakshi%20says%20Son%20Rise%20was%20a%20step%20in%20the%20same%20direction.%20The%20narrative%20isn%E2%80%99t%20preachy%3B%20there%20is%20no%20moral%20policing.%20Instead%2C%20the%20cinematic%20masterpiece%20makes%20the%20most%20of%20its%2050%20minutes%20to%20leave%20the%20audience%20with%20some%20food%20for%20thought.%20The%20film%20uncovers%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F276654%2Funique-wedding-tradition-rituals-breaking-norms-patriarchy-atheist-couple%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egendered%20realities%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Haryana%20by%20shedding%20light%20on%20the%20changemakers%20instead%20of%20the%20perpetrators.%20And%20this%20is%20what%20sets%20it%20apart.%20It%20beckons%20you%20to%20look%20towards%20the%20light.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FSonRise_poster_page-0001_11zon-1727704960-500x707.jpg%5C