)%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Global%20SABRE%20Award%20(2022)%20%E2%80%94%20the%20validation%20Bakshi%20values%20most%20comes%20when%20men%20approach%20her%20and%20say%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhat%E2%80%99s%20happening%20is%20not%20right.%20What%20can%20we%20do%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20heart%20of%20every%20film%20of%20hers%20is%20a%20wish%2C%20a%20hope%2C%20a%20prayer%20for%20a%20world%20where%20men%20become%20allies%20and%20women%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20fear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Gender%20inequality%20is%20not%20limited%20to%20hinterlands%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20%3Cem%3Edhoti%20%3C%2Fem%3E(wraparound%20cloth%20worn%20around%20the%20legs)%20and%20chequered%20scarf%20protect%20the%20men%20of%20Haryana%2C%20as%20they%20sit%20in%20clans%2C%20sipping%20hot%20cups%20of%20%3Cem%3Echai%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20camera%20pans%20to%20the%20oldest%20among%20the%20group%2C%20possibly%20in%20his%20sixties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20don%E2%80%99t%20let%20girls%20be%20born%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20reaffirms%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20reputation%20for%20female%20foeticides.%20Another%20from%20the%20group%20chips%20in%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20do%20ultrasounds%20to%20peek%20into%20the%20womb.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAre%20%E2%80%98they%E2%80%99%20successful%20in%20these%20killings%3F%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20look%20to%20the%20men%20on%20screen%20for%20answers.%20Statistics%20point%20us%20in%20the%20direction%20of%20a%20skewed%20sex%20ratio.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201901%2C%20the%20state%20had%20867%20females%20per%201%2C000%20males%20in%20its%20total%20population%2C%20as%20per%20the%20Statistical%20Handbook%20of%20Haryana%202020-21.%20Over%20100%20years%20later%2C%20as%20per%20Census%202011%2C%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20sex%20ratio%20remained%20equal