alked%20up%20to%20her%20with%20a%20piece%20of%20news%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CI%20know%20of%20a%20farmer%20who%20is%20in%20an%20arranged%20marriage%20with%20a%20gang%20rape%20victim.%E2%80%9D%20Bakshi%20spent%20the%20next%20several%20days%20tracking%20him%20down.%20When%20she%20finally%20did%2C%20her%20first%20question%20to%20him%20was%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20did%20you%20agree%20to%20this%3F%E2%80%9D%20And%20the%20farmer%20answered%20her%20question%20with%20one%20of%20his%20own%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20not%3F%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%9CThe%20shame%20is%20not%20hers%2C%20it%20is%20ours.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20his%20wife%2C%20the%20survivor%20who%20was%20raped%20by%20eight%20men%20and%20sentenced%20to%20a%20life%20of%20looking%20over%20her%20shoulder%20every%20time%20she%20left%20home%2C%20things%20took%20a%20turn%20after%20the%20documentary%20got%20UN%20recognition.%20Recalling%20that%20full-circle%20moment%2C%20Bakshi%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20film%20screening%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekhap%20%3C%2Fem%3Eleader%20stood%20behind%20her%2C%20issuing%20a%20silent%20warning%20to%20anyone%20who%20dared%20to%20touch%20her.%E2%80%9D%20That%20is%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F170476%2Findia-oscar-winner-period-documentary-winner%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epower%20of%20a%20documentary%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20she%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98The%20issue%20is%20the%20same%3B%20the%20packaging%20is%20different%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20article%20exploring%20how%20the%20needle%20is%20moving%20in%20favour%20of%20Indian%20documentary%20filmmakers%20found%20that%20while%20filmmakers%20engage%20with%20the%20international%20industry%2C%20they%20are%20finding%20it%20harder%20than%20ever%20