image-76-1727772570-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-76-1727772570-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-76-1727772570-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-76-1727772570-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-368184%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMangrove%20plantation%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20estimates%20by%20L%26amp%3BT%2C%20there%20is%20a%20potential%20for%20almost%2020%20to%2030%20tonnes%20of%20carbon%20being%20sequestered%20per%20hectare%20of%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMangroves%20play%20a%20significant%20role%20in%20the%20economic%20activities%20of%20the%20local%20community%20and%20therefore%2C%20the%20locals%20from%20the%20coastal%20area%20of%20Katpor%20were%20actively%20involved%20in%20the%20entire%20process.%20The%20GEC%20collaborated%20with%20a%20local%20community-based%20organisation%2C%20Katpor%20Tamvar%20Vikas%20Samiti%2C%20to%20oversee%20the%20project.%20The%20villagers%20were%20trained%20in%20every%20aspect%20of%20mangrove%20planting%2C%20from%20developing%20saplings%20to%20managing%20and%20maintaining%20the%20plantations.%20The%20GEC%20also%20raised%20awareness%20among%20the%20villagers%20about%20the%20environmental%20importance%20of%20mangroves%2C%20ensuring%20that%20they%20were%20well-equipped%20to%20manage%20and%20maintain%20the%20afforestation%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20course%20of%20the%20five%20to%20six-year%20project%2C%20more%20than%2010%2C000%20workdays%20were%20generated%2C%20providing%20significant%20employment%20opportunities.%20Many%20women%20from%20the%20community%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20various%20processes%20%E2%80%94%20including%20seed%20collection%2C%20manual%20sowing%2C%20nursery%20management%2C%20and%20more%20%E2%80%94%20contributing%20to%20both%20the%20project%E2%80%99s%20success%20and%20their%20own%20economic%20empowerment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBefore%20the%20mangrove%20plantation%2C%20the%20area%20was%20a%20wasteland.%20Farmers%20faced%20a%20tough%20time%20as%20yield%20was%20low%20due%20to%20high%20salinity%20in%20the%20soil%20and%20salty%20winds%20leading%20to%20crop%20damage%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rathod.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-77-1727772853.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Babubhai%20Rathod%2C%20former%20sarpanch%20and%20a%20resident%20of%20Karanj.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-77-1727772853.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-77-1727772853-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-77-1727772853-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-77-1727772853-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-77-1727772853-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-368189%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBabubhai%20Rathod%2C%20former%20sarpanch%20and%20a%20resident%20of%20Karanj.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20plantation%E2%80%99s%20completion%20in%202015%2C%20it%20has%20brought%20a%20transformative%20change%20to%20the%20lives%20of%20the%20farmers.%20In%20these%20two%20villages%2C%20farmers%20typically%20grow%20crops%20such%20as%20rice%2C%20maize%2C%20pigeon%20pea%20(%3Cem%3Etuvar%20dal%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20and%20fruits%20like%20mangoes.%20The%20mangrove%20initiative%20has%20helped%20improve%20their%20livelihoods%20and%20agricultural%20practices.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20plantation%20prevented%20saltwater%20from%20reaching%20the%20farm%2C%20preventing%20crop%20damage.%20The%20quality%20of%20crops%20has%20increased%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rathod.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMangroves%20also%20facilitate%20prawn%20and%20shrimp%20farming%20by%20acting%20as%20a%20natural%20barrier%20against%20tidal%20surges.%20And%20besides%20the%20benefits%20to%20the%20farmers%2C%20the%20environmental%20benefits%20of%20this%20plantation%20are%20immense.%20This%20initiative%20is%20also%20improving%20coastal%20resilience%2C%20protecting%20farmland%20from%20erosion%2C%20and%20ensuring%20long-term%20environmental%20sustainability%20through%20carbon%20sequestration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMoving%20towards%20a%20better%20world%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Blue%20Carbon%20initiative%20is%20part%20of%20L%26amp%3BT%E2%80%99s%20larger%20vision%20of%20working%20towards%20a%20better%20planet.%20Beyond%20mangroves%2C%20the%20company%20is%20working%20towards%20ambitious%20environmental%20goals%2C%20including%20achieving%20carbon%20neutrality%20by%202040%20(ahead%20of%20the%20Paris%20Agreement)%20and%20water%20neutrality%20by%202035.%20The%20company%20has%20planted%20four%20million%20saplings%20in%20FY%202023-24%2C%202.5%20million%20of%20which%20were%20planted%20in%20August%202023%20through%20%E2%80%98Project%20GreenHands%E2%80%99%20across%20559%20project%20sites%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Anup%20Sahay%2C%20Head%20%E2%80%93%20Corporate%20Strategy%20and%20Special%20Initiatives%2C%20L%26amp%3BT.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-c